Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:11.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,My First Errand. {\alphaFF\t(2317,2317,\alpha0)}Cute overload special.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,611.333)}Hakusanrenpou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:17.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,My First Errand has been on the air for 27 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:19.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,27 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:21.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We've been all around from the north of Hokkaido down to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:27.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's easy to think we've run out of places, but there are still places to explore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:28.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,There are?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:30.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here at Ishikawa prefecture the water is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:36.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The water flows from the snowy mountain tops of Hakusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:38.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and it is called "the water of life".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:44.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's our first time coming here and \Nit will be the first errand for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:47.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's wearing sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:53.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:53.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:56.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ao is almost 3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:56.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,2 years and 11 months?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao and her red sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:04.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is a nursery school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:07.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is also where Ao is enrolled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:13.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is in her 9th month of pregnancy, so Ao will become a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,- I see. \N - An important time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:15.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She keeps asking when he will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:21.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as an experience before becoming \Na big sister she will go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:25.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she's still 2 years old. Will she be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.15,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get the stem? We will use it \Nto make scrambled soup. With tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot to buy tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to buy scrambled tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:42.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Scrambled tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:46.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this tofu shop they boil soy milk and make tofu from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:52.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Scrambled tofu is served before being made firm from weights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,Absolutely tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's fluffly and delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:00.43,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.18,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:03.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrambled tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrambled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Scrambled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.80,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Scrambled tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:19.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The tofu is 250 yen. The mother put 500 yen in her wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also go and visit the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:29.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From the 500 yen she will get her\N change and can use it at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:29.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:31.63,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Heading off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy tofu and visit the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the same route as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:49.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Buying scrambled tofu, getting change from the 500 yen and then visiting the shrine where she was told to give one coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.39,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,So amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,- She's motivated. \N- She's so focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:05.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's merely 2 years and 11 months\N old and moves with small steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.33,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:09.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is she not getting lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.81,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:16.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one who is getting lonely is the \Nmother who keeps watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop is straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:26.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, she wants in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A shortcut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameramen are chasing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are hurrying after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as planned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:44.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Actually, this neighborhood is full of houses and there are plenty of secret pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:50.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since she walks around every morning with her grandmother her mother is confident she can find the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,So she knows what she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is she worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The shopping part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about it worries you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she doesn't have much experience with it, I'm not sure if she can pay properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she's still heading straight for the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She looks so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.35,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The house with a chimney blows its smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A house with a chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, the ladder. It's used to clear the snow in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is an area of the most prominent heavy snow fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:35.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Around town there are many ways to get rid of the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:35.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.39,Studio,,0,0,0,,How smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:43.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big crossing. She will arrive\N at the shop if she goes left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:51.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She trots along when crossing. But she went that way. That's not where the shop is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She should know the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are being played by a 2 year and 11 month old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,Run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where Ao is heading is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.14,Studio,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:08.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wants to visit the shrine first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why is she taking her backpack off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:15.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's taking out a blue towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's grabbing the shaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:25.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is "the water of life" from the mountain top of Hakusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:34.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's scooping it with the shaku. \NShe knows exactly how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:41.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Grabbing it closely and... perfectly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,She knows exactly how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:48.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one most moved by it is the cameraman close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the purification, the stairs lead to the front of the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:06:01.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For a 2 year and 11 month old each step is a hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does she know the rites of visiting a shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:10.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh, she's taking her backpack off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:13.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, she's taking out her wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:19.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's only one 500 yen coin in it which is intended for the tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's putting it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- She put it in. \N- She put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.07,Studio,,0,0,0,,What will she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:33.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's praying with 500 yen worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:45.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I hope the baby will be big and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:49.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I hope that I will become a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:53.22,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I love my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:03.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her wishes echoed throughout the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.50,Studio,,0,0,0,,What will she do about the tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:10.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's leaving the shrine and heading towards the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:17.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has arrived at the scrambled tofu shop with an empty wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,What will she do? She doesn't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She opens the automatic doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.24,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old man who is always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We didn't have tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.43,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We didn't have tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.40,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We ran out of the usual tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The same tofu as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.41,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Scrambled tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:43.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,She remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.51,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This one? Which one was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:51.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She found the scrambled tofu however...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be 250 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.40,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I don't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't? Could you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:05.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You don't have money? What will you do? Without money you can't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:08.69,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't receive any money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:12.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's trying to get the crew to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:18.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go back to your mom and... What will you do? You can't buy it without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if she's asked what she intends to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.97,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go back home and retrieve some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.86,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to go home empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old guy figures out a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And get one like these from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:47.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A 500 yen coin. Like the one \Nshe donated at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back home and get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.63,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.22,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are amazing. I will keep the tofu for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:01.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Haha, can't believe it all came to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.71,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get the tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,Because she doesn't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:16.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She understands that you have to pay money to get things, but she doesn't understand how change works.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right. She's only 2 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:22.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's still energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:24.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You were fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:29.96,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tofu   money   didn't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.67,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,No money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She couldn't explain it well. \NShe's only 2 years and 11 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What about the scrambled tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,No scrambled tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The scrambled tofu that Aochan loves so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:51.27,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,For Aochan, this kind of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:56.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's so much she wants to convey \Nbut she can't find the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother tries to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I was told the money wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you told the money isn't enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the money go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The money disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.17,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you give it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:17.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask me "who" it's not like I've seen the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:22.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,To the shrine. I gave it to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You did? So you also rang the bell? \NAnd then clapped your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:31.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. She gave the money and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I didn't ring the bell at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:35.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:43.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like Aochan is saying. She didn't actually ring the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:46.49,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I didn't ring the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:50.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a puzzling conversation it turned into.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:54.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother thinks of changing her way of asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aochan, which one did you go to first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.22,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to ring the bell first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:00.94,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Ring the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:06.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,, I see. So that's what it's about. \NI finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:10.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time she's getting 3 100 yen coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go and get tofu. \NCan you do your best once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.42,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can do my best once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright. Her energy is coming back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Toooooot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:25.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her fart shows that she's come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amazing character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been waiting with the tofu in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You did? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:35.71,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I had money put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old man is the one who's nervous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She brought 300 yen this time. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she only put out one coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!? Only got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One of them was meant for the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.04,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there were more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How great. There were more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your change is 50 yen. \NCan you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,See? This is what's called change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't drop it. \NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,Alright, she bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:29.50,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.50,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I didn't ring the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:35.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's been on her mind that she didn't get to ring it the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.08,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is she going again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time she went directly towards the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:41.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's back at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,I'm home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.65,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh, she did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ring ring ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:55.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today she's ringing it with all her might.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:03.21,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Motheeeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.89,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.93,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I did. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you purchase it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:24.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The scrambled tofu she bought \Nis served in miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:27.05,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:30.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father came back during his lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,, It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrambled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.61,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "scrambled please"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:41.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The taste of scrambled tofu that \N you bought yourself is exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.45,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Aochan will become a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aochan, you will become a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You will be a cherished sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Nom nom cherished nom nom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:53.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She even asked the gods for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:55.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then 2 months later...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:01.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The wish she loudly asked for came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Isn't it great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can a single clip contain this much happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, it was truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, wasn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us briefly introduce you to our guests
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Itou, the archetypical Japanese father\Nand Suzu the ideal young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Kadono Takuzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and next to her is Kadono Takuzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:34.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,Male actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- What did you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's completely cute. From \Nwhat she does to what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If the old guy at the tofu shop gave her the tofu and said, "Your mom can pay me later.", we wouldn't have gotten that fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:58.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,402.572)}Father of a 5 year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so mature. She even knows the shortcuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thus perplexing the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- And she raises her hand when crossing the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's much more mature than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the next errand. With only a years difference the mission changes completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(646.857,561.429)}Ishikawa ● Hakusan city
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:15.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here we find the talkative girl who is almost 4 year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:21.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Isn't the reason she knows many words because she reads so many picture books?" her mother says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:25.41,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1059.429,208.286)}Mio\N3 years 9 months
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:31.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since she's already 3 and a big sister\N she frequents this place often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:38.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Before going to bed she always reads one picture book and they even enact it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:45.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this bookshelve there is only on book that hasn't been borrowed by the library. A book they've written themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:49.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By dad and mom: Thank you Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:54.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A picture book from when Mio was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,So much love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:16:01.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now she's showing the newest creation: \NMio's First Errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:10.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's not complete yet. They will \N change it after today's errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I read a bit for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:12.92,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,See? It says: My first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:21.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's been reading the book before bed for several days to teach her how to go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:25.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The soon-to-be 4 year old Mio will go on her first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:28.22,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,True, today is my first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:33.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Give me a mackerel from Ishikawa with its head and guts removed, filleted into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If there aren't any?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.72,Studio,,0,0,0,,Sounds complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:41.95,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If there aren't any then dottybacks, sailfin or sandfish and if possible, from Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if possible. Definitely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:46.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's buying locally sourced ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:52.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And if they don't have any then she shouldn't purchase anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:56.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They only buy fresh laid Yanagihara eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore... okra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.16,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Okra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And nameko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:04.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Those two weren't included in the picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:10.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She remembers the things in the picture book well but she's still only 3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You have money here and the loyalty card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,You are even making her use the loyalty card?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:19.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a simple route along the huge street to get to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:28.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she needs to get mackerel from Ishikawa prefecture, eggs from Yanagihara, tofu, lotus root, okra, nameko mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even adults would forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.62,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Heading off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:37.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She picked the straw hat at the shop\N because she thought it was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:43.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And she likes to walk without socks which she is used to so her mother lets her do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.42,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:51.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's nice autumn weather which the picture book didn't mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh!? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:55.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:58.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman is surprised that she spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:03.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All by yourself? You are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:03.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm going on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:05.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Only 3 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:08.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's rare to find such a talkative 3 year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:17.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since the conversation could go on the camera man moves away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:20.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mio no longer has anyone to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:25.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait... is she going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's running home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,A gust of lonely air hit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.04,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,You didn't draw me a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A map? You need a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:38.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know how to read a map or characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:47.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She always has to remember. \NThat's why her memory is so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:53.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She changed hats. This one is a camouflaged patterned. Ready for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:58.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's adding a smiley face so that\N she can know which one is her left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Remember to turn left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:03.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I will be here for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:08.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She departs with a new map and a smiley face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? That face. Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is she feeling lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Back to the spot where she last turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:21.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,She won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can't seem to cross this iron grate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:31.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Turning at this corner she will\N no longer be able to see her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,Because she can't see back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's 50 meters from her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In her mother's book it says: \N"It's alright. Do your best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And to cross the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She couldn't do like it says in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.78,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:53.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's walking back crying unlike in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:01.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother shows her determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you, Mio. \NI didn't ask anyone else to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be good if you don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:15.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I want to be a better big sister since my little sister was born." is what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a bit too optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but she does want to be helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is how she wants to be seen by her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:25.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You will soon be 4 so you can definitely go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.26,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Big sister bye."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.06,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's lonely but.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:46.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.80,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely but I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely but I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you are lonely then go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I want to become a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:00.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.35,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of {\i1}I{\i0} go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:10.26,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.54,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Of {\i1}I{\i0} go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The start of a big sisters journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:21.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,Her sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That iron grate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.15,Studio,,0,0,0,,Here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.15,Studio,,0,0,0,,Here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,Take a step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:28.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is the borderline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Left, left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go along the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:39.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister has finally crossed the iron grate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.35,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if your sister left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The map for good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you cry then wipe the tears with your towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.30,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:56.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's lonely but she will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:02.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On a day with beautiful cirrocumulus clouds​.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:05.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Surrounded by lucious green.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:09.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's walking way over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:17.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When grandpa came to visit from the countryside, she remembered walking down this road and singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:25.46,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The moon, came out out, the moon came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:25.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,Because he's a grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:26.95,Studio,,0,0,0,,What an old song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:27.53,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,605)}A yoi yoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:28.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has learned this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:34.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,600)}The chimney is so high up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:44.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Surely the moon will be covered in smoke. Yoi Yoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:40.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,She remembers it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is she dancing the second chorus?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:51.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:55.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While lost in song she's already arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:58.61,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.27,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Eggs and lotus root.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:04.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I must buy a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,Her energy is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:12.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This supermarket is for locally sourced fish and vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:11.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:15.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was asked to get many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:17.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How much of it will she remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:18.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,She can't read yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:19.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,Can she do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:23.42,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Did you give birth to eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:29.60,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,599)}Yanagihara eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:30.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Amazing, she remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:32.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are some?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:34.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are freshly laid today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:37.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since her birth she's only had these Yanagihara eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:40.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since Mio has seen them last.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about other shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.21,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to buy handaga tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You want hankata tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.18,0:23:52.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This tofu has a hard exterior but is soft on the inside. She also got this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:55.40,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Lotus root.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotus root?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:58.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her memory is amazing. \NShe instantly remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:01.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not only does she remember their name...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.60,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's better if they have many internodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:08.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's a housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:12.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She chooses the one that seems to be high in mineral content.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.46,0:24:14.12,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:17.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the book:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.38,0:24:20.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:22.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do you have mackerel from Ishikawa prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gut it and remove the heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:26.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I want 2 fillets, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.58,0:24:26.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.49,0:24:29.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what it says. I wonder if she can say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:30.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,Even adults would forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.64,0:24:31.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,Even adults would forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.76,0:24:36.71,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Do you have mackerel from Ishikawa prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.60,0:24:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.98,0:24:41.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.35,0:24:43.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Filleted into two, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.29,0:24:44.89,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Cut their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.89,0:24:46.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.00,0:24:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay with just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:50.51,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.67,0:24:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One cut into two fillets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.51,0:24:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.64,0:24:52.34,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.24,0:24:53.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,I'm moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:55.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was able to say it with vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.18,0:24:57.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She didn't ask them to gut it but
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:25:00.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she asked them to fillet it so the guts are already removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.32,0:25:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.29,0:25:04.22,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Only the mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.31,0:25:05.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,Only the mackerel. Haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.99,0:25:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.36,0:25:10.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.76,0:25:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:16.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She even ad libbed a thanks outside of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.24,0:25:18.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Only okura and nameko left.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.00,0:25:20.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.14,0:25:21.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She went to the cashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.56,0:25:22.47,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.99,0:25:23.96,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.96,0:25:26.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It looks like she forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.40,0:25:29.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother just added those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:31.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They were not in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:33.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.52,0:25:36.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Paying 2000 and receiving 940 yen back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:39.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's extraordinary that a 3 year old can do all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.89,0:25:41.79,Studio,,0,0,0,,It is. Truly extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.96,0:25:44.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Drinking cold bancha.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.86,0:25:47.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then she remembers...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:49.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.60,0:25:52.00,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to buy nameko mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You need nameko?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.00,0:25:53.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.11,0:25:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you to the nameko. \NLet's go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.96,0:25:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right th..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.31,0:25:58.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mom also...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.06,0:26:01.01,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, I will also buy okura.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.10,0:26:02.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She remembered the okura.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.03,0:26:05.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She remembered everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.40,0:26:08.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Small nameko would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.55,0:26:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Small would be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.74,0:26:12.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since there are sizes of nameko.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.24,0:26:14.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big ones are for stir-frying.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.96,0:26:17.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the small ones are good in miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.46,0:26:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are various.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.75,0:26:20.83,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.67,0:26:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.88,0:26:22.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, these are good with miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.52,0:26:25.67,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And okura?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okura is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:27.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the last item. Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.17,0:26:31.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They usually can be found here but are sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.15,0:26:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have anymore today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.28,0:26:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.48,0:26:41.35,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,While there were eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.35,0:26:43.82,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,there were no okura. What a rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.01,0:26:48.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's true. Usually there are okura.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.80,0:26:52.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The hat on tight. Job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.86,0:26:54.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,Marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.75,0:26:59.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A suspicious cloud surrounds the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.99,0:27:04.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She talked with many and purchased a lot. Now she only needs to head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.09,0:27:07.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:08.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's dawdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.88,0:27:13.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,My legs hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.94,0:27:18.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The book didn't mention that \N the groceries would be heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.11,0:27:20.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or that her legs would hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.06,0:27:39.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The road along the rice field.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.38,0:27:44.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's not singing the Tanko-bushi song this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.70,0:27:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.05,0:27:48.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's 3. And a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.92,0:27:54.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She struggles between wanting to exert herself and wanting to be treated sweetly like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.14,0:27:56.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her heart is wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.90,0:27:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.25,0:28:00.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did she reach her limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.23,0:28:02.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.52,0:28:04.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her tears stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.32,0:28:06.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.47,0:28:11.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,What is that? The white thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.36,0:28:14.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's bad. She spotted our drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.61,0:28:15.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,She spotted the drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.21,0:28:16.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.16,0:28:17.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.75,0:28:20.54,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It goes up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.54,0:28:24.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It took her mind off the heaviness of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.61,0:28:25.96,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.34,0:28:27.66,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.66,0:28:30.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An old lady is picking flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.05,0:28:31.53,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.53,0:28:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.01,0:28:33.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.30,0:28:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.65,0:28:38.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not the afternoon yet but the old lady goes along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.04,0:28:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:41.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can I??
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.57,0:28:43.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.28,0:28:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink and orange? \NThat's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.65,0:28:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want only 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.82,0:28:50.88,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.37,0:28:53.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.54,0:28:56.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you the tears have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.60,0:29:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big sister is doing her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.01,0:29:19.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As soon as she sees the house \Nshe lets out all the tears she held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.52,0:29:25.52,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.67,0:29:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.35,0:29:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.34,0:29:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.04,0:29:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.51,0:29:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.26,0:29:37.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The important words to tell mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.93,0:29:41.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,They didn't have okura.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.45,0:29:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have okura?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.38,0:29:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bothering her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.04,0:29:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's make tofu and nameko miso soup then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.14,0:29:52.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wants to be held like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:56.12,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mommy. This is a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.12,0:29:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.38,0:29:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought me a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.49,0:30:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.82,0:30:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.80,0:30:04.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. The picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.31,0:30:06.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Must complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.26,0:30:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, tell me how you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.76,0:30:12.91,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,I missed you, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:15.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because it was so tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.12,0:30:17.15,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If you write it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.15,0:30:20.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, a lot was added to the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.06,0:30:23.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That she cried from loneliness before departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.78,0:30:26.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And that she sang Tanko-bushi with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.10,0:30:29.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or that she received flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.56,0:30:32.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.77,0:30:37.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mom, you've completed a great book.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.11,0:30:41.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Well... It's all thanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.43,0:30:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.68,0:30:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What a marvelous errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.48,0:30:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a top score.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.37,0:30:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A top score.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking aimlessly at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.14,0:30:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(265.143,520.286)}Mother of boys of these ages
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.20,0:30:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The she remembered it all and to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.43,0:31:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When she said: "They don't have okura"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.95,0:31:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's truly laudable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.07,0:31:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go back to those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.09,0:31:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When she asked the shopkeeper
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.58,0:31:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,did you give birth to eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.18,0:31:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.18,0:31:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Things not written in the book are bound to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.11,0:31:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,During the errand of the youngest of 3 brothers the shop will be thrown into disarray.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.34,0:31:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1011.428,147.714)}Tochi ● Tochigi City
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.56,0:31:36.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here's a house that likes to keep thing neat and tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.83,0:31:39.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Time for cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.58,0:31:42.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Inside the house looks like a showroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.75,0:31:47.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother's philosophy is to put everything orderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.45,0:31:54.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everything has its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.63,0:31:56.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.62,0:32:02.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The youngest of 3 at 3 years and 9 months, Masashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.54,0:32:06.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The other two haven't returned from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.08,0:32:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.75,0:32:13.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's a place in the storage room that she isn't satisfied with.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.35,0:32:14.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.20,0:32:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up Mr. Masashi. \NMama wants another of those baskets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.71,0:32:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What if there were 3 or 4 of those baskets here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.23,0:32:24.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.90,0:32:28.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. Measuring it so he can purchase the right size.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.90,0:32:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,About this high.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.67,0:32:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and purchase them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.84,0:32:33.84,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,About thi...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.90,0:32:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:36.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And adding an errand for the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.04,0:32:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For remuneration let's get the expensive bluefin tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.93,0:32:42.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does he understand "remuneration"?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.16,0:32:44.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,530)}Toro
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.05,0:32:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Toro (the fatty belly meat of the tuna)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.00,0:32:46.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does he understand toro?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.45,0:32:51.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For remuneration (as a reward) he will get toro.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.67,0:32:56.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On the way back from the fishmonger there is a home center close to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.19,0:32:59.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was asked to buy 3 white baskets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.26,0:33:00.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.33,0:33:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help your mother in cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.44,0:33:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.30,0:33:04.42,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.42,0:33:06.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was raining until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.07,0:33:09.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So she gave him rubber boots in case of puddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.57,0:33:11.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.14,0:33:13.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was looking forward to going on errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.81,0:33:14.30,Studio,,0,0,0,,So he wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.96,0:33:16.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Usually his brothers are asked to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.07,0:33:19.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The third in the row who is expected less of.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.72,0:33:22.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's called cute and treated like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.97,0:33:26.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Masashi dislikes those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.14,0:33:28.76,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.03,0:33:31.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today is the first time he is being relied on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.81,0:33:33.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The stakes are high, third son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.53,0:33:34.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.94,0:33:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.45,0:33:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.54,0:33:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.17,0:33:41.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.94,0:33:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.64,0:33:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you usually with your brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.61,0:33:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.59,0:33:48.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Toro as remuneration, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.86,0:33:52.52,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The similar thing as tuna, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.52,0:33:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuna and salmon?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.79,0:33:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Both?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.42,0:33:59.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He neither understood remuneration or toro.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.86,0:34:01.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Poor thing. It changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.98,0:34:05.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When the old man heard the word similar he gave him the same thing his mom usually buys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.80,0:34:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.10,0:34:08.63,Studio,,0,0,0,,What about the toro?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.63,0:34:11.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The lean tuna meat and salmon. Not exactly renummeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.40,0:34:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be 1080 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.97,0:34:14.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ended up being cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.76,0:34:17.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This triumphant face.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.24,0:34:19.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a nice face.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.44,0:34:21.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It will do even if it isn't toro.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.30,0:34:22.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.11,0:34:23.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop owners are observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.90,0:34:25.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,Eaten together isn't it like Toro anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.44,0:34:30.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,He looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.57,0:34:33.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,With great delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.49,0:34:36.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He picked something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.96,0:34:38.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A single leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.67,0:34:44.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now for the 3 white baskets.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.99,0:34:46.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's arrived at the home center.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.39,0:34:47.26,Studio,,0,0,0,,Going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.76,0:34:49.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's so spacious inside. Will he find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.64,0:34:55.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,About 19000 stock units are sold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:58.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finding things can be hard even for adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.02,0:35:01.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,Will he get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.65,0:35:02.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Isn't it faster to ask a store worker?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.95,0:35:05.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He should ask: "Where are the wide baskets?"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.07,0:35:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.56,0:35:07.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's the store manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.48,0:35:10.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Pigeons
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.08,0:35:17.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The same pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.93,0:35:13.18,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The same pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.30,0:35:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(608,103.454)}Pigeon: hato \NHeart: ha-to\NBasket: hako
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.20,0:35:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.18,0:35:14.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Baskets for storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.87,0:35:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you come to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.48,0:35:18.07,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Pigeon
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.07,0:35:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.67,0:35:22.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The same one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.92,0:35:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The same one?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.04,0:35:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.09,0:35:25.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, he shouldn't have brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.58,0:35:27.26,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.26,0:35:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.26,0:35:29.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.08,0:35:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.31,0:35:29.33,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.45,0:35:30.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,The store manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.81,0:35:31.65,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Pi-geon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.65,0:35:34.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not a heart. A basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.90,0:35:36.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,Manager, you don't sell hearts, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.54,0:35:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try and look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.99,0:35:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for a heart-like thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.59,0:35:43.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.73,0:35:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what color?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.05,0:35:51.55,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.35,0:35:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You came looking for a green thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.55,0:35:53.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The green leaf is confusing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.84,0:35:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have green things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.36,0:35:58.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not like they have green hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.09,0:35:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.83,0:36:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heart shaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.08,0:36:05.53,Studio,,0,0,0,,They did have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:05.53,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.45,0:36:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.62,0:36:09.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,They did have such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.75,0:36:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a green heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.54,0:36:14.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.01,0:36:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.38,0:36:16.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,- That's great. \N- Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.79,0:36:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have green things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.63,0:36:20.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The store manager is focused on finding green things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.91,0:36:22.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's not even green.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.63,0:36:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Green. What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.28,0:36:25.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are so many green things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.71,0:36:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.37,0:36:28.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.97,0:36:30.34,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.34,0:36:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides the color
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.08,0:36:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.86,0:36:35.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.50,0:36:39.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In spite of being right next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.33,0:36:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.85,0:36:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,can you ask your mother and come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.54,0:36:46.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.06,0:36:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, go and ask and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.78,0:36:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.05,0:36:53.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He decides on asking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.72,0:36:55.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their house is close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.73,0:36:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what he needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.04,0:37:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.74,0:37:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.44,0:37:03.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.34,0:37:05.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's on us. Thanks for being polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.23,0:37:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.91,0:37:10.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though he managed to buy the tuna he returns dejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.55,0:37:14.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.42,0:37:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma-.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.69,0:37:18.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I titn't unterstant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.74,0:37:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(609.455,45.272)}He makes the same mistake here of pronouncing the k sound as t.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.02,0:37:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go to the home center?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.26,0:37:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.58,0:37:23.49,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Green pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.49,0:37:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You said green basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.20,0:37:30.27,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And he hear{\i1}t{\i0} it as heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.87,0:37:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He heard it as heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.27,0:37:32.84,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But it's not heart is what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.84,0:37:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you said it's not heart he didn't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.79,0:37:37.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So his mother thought of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.13,0:37:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You explained that this is a green basket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.11,0:37:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But mama wants white.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.38,0:37:46.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. It should be white.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.60,0:37:49.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I accidentally said green.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.97,0:37:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time say white.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.82,0:37:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to say basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.71,0:37:54.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,595)}I couldn't say taro (yam).
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.14,0:37:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to say ka like in karasu (crow).
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.03,0:37:58.86,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Ta as in tarasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.86,0:38:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.28,0:38:06.67,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Tarasu why do you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.67,0:38:10.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Ta as in tarasu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.71,0:38:12.58,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.58,0:38:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ka not ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.01,0:38:20.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Masashi who can't say ka is {\i1}ka{\i0}ming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.32,0:38:22.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The store manager was waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.67,0:38:25.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I went and came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.66,0:38:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You went and asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.66,0:38:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(616.728,62.726)}Again the difference between "went" and "ask" is "k".\NThe manager picked up on it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.57,0:38:25.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best, manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.72,0:38:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.39,0:38:32.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,If you turn where the slippers are then it should be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.06,0:38:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning where the slippers are?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.90,0:38:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The slippers are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.93,0:38:39.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Looking for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you use it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.66,0:38:46.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,To put things in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.79,0:38:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To put things in?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.08,0:38:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you put in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.60,0:38:49.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\i1}T{\i0}(p)aper {\i1}t{\i0}and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.35,0:38:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Accumulations?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.37,0:38:51.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taper (paper).
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.32,0:38:52.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You put paper in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.68,0:38:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taper!?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.69,0:38:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.30,0:38:55.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.72,0:38:57.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taper.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:38:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You put that in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.99,0:38:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,659.091)}If it's something to stor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.74,0:39:00.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,White.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.42,0:39:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,White?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.53,0:39:02.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.79,0:39:02.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,He noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.59,0:39:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.21,0:39:03.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.90,0:39:05.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.76,0:39:06.83,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,591)}Those are plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.76,0:39:07.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dude, he's not here for plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.40,0:39:08.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It can't be folded.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.30,0:39:12.00,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It can't be folded.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.30,0:39:12.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be foldable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.00,0:39:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.81,0:39:16.24,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A white s{\i1}t{\i0}uare.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.24,0:39:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A white square?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.08,0:39:20.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He understood "square".
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.21,0:39:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not disposable chopsticks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.80,0:39:24.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why disposable chopsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.38,0:39:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a lunch box?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.45,0:39:27.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While white and square that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.45,0:39:28.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.22,0:39:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you, store manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.12,0:39:32.29,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It can't be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.29,0:39:34.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Can't be folded.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.96,0:39:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be folded nor eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.81,0:39:36.46,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's turned into a puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.83,0:39:37.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Right where they are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.81,0:39:40.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Down the aisle around the slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.60,0:39:40.83,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.10,0:39:43.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There they are the white taro (yam)... oops, I meant baskets.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.07,0:39:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.15,0:39:48.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite it being further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.57,0:39:50.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.54,0:39:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.83,0:39:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.26,0:39:56.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He noticed something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.10,0:39:59.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.13,0:39:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.90,0:40:01.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A basket of this height.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.59,0:40:02.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.50,0:40:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama told you to bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.99,0:40:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.63,0:40:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Show your detective skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.83,0:40:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The hint is too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.48,0:40:16.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But you use this with pencils.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.97,0:40:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You use it with pencils?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.59,0:40:21.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Borrowed from his brothers' stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.77,0:40:23.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An irrelevant piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.24,0:40:24.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,A ruler, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.76,0:40:27.80,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best store manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.74,0:40:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go back and ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.86,0:40:29.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.58,0:40:31.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,This turned into the store managers' errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.71,0:40:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you? Go and ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.72,0:40:33.25,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.25,0:40:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more, go back and then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.24,0:40:38.74,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.93,0:40:46.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why can't the man find him a taro (yam).
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.00,0:40:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.25,0:40:51.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has kids in primary and junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.99,0:40:54.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've outgrown that phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.12,0:40:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.57,0:40:57.48,Studio,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.97,0:40:59.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Masashi is returning home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.11,0:41:00.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,Having so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.96,0:41:02.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mother is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.15,0:41:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.37,0:41:08.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.94,0:41:10.05,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.05,0:41:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.82,0:41:15.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,They didn't have a single thing to put {\i1}t{\i0}aper in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.93,0:41:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "for putting paper in"?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.36,0:41:21.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother naturally hears taper as paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.57,0:41:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Basket, basket, basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.73,0:41:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Say basket while you walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.49,0:41:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Basket, basket, basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.47,0:41:28.77,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taro, taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.77,0:41:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.18,0:41:36.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite trying to say "basket" why doesn't the manager listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.55,0:41:40.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's because he's not able to say basket at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.15,0:41:44.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The store manager is on Masashi duty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.66,0:41:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(609.455,45.272)}Again he meant to say asked not came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.94,0:41:46.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I went and came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.91,0:41:47.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best, manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.39,0:41:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.04,0:41:47.88,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.88,0:41:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's around the slippers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.39,0:41:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.40,0:41:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.63,0:41:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she tell you to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.85,0:41:58.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,She said taro (yam).
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.37,0:41:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Barrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.14,0:41:59.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.57,0:42:00.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.45,0:42:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Haro?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.37,0:42:02.77,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.04,0:42:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taro?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.04,0:42:05.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Stuare taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.14,0:42:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Barrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.78,0:42:09.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They turned where the slippers are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.41,0:42:11.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:13.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,To.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.25,0:42:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What if {\alpha&FF}you try to say it slowly?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.70,0:42:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you try to say it slowly?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.69,0:42:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.21,0:42:22.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.24,0:42:22.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's back to pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.09,0:42:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.48,0:42:28.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Something that you put things in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.91,0:42:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You put things in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.10,0:42:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.53,0:42:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.10,0:42:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.77,0:42:33.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.85,0:42:34.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.14,0:42:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not pigeon but basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.42,0:42:39.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.11,0:42:40.26,Studio,,0,0,0,,A breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.41,0:42:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.22,0:42:42.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.62,0:42:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.88,0:42:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.72,0:42:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.87,0:42:48.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.22,0:42:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.87,0:42:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This? Did we find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.49,0:42:53.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,He looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.13,0:42:55.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He found the taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.31,0:42:56.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.43,0:43:00.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,, Manager, about the height...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.83,0:43:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the height right for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.42,0:43:05.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.89,0:43:08.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The height is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.22,0:43:10.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.57,0:43:13.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He finally bought it. Three white taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.64,0:43:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.50,0:43:17.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The manager's eyes are gleaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.78,0:43:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.67,0:43:22.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.32,0:43:26.11,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.01,0:43:25.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:25.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.56,0:43:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's shake hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.64,0:43:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.70,0:43:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.81,0:43:34.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,The manager is such a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.70,0:43:36.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's no longer a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.77,0:43:39.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He executed his errand properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.41,0:43:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He bought it. He bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.91,0:43:48.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.85,0:43:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma-.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.67,0:43:57.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His proud smiling face is dazzling his mother's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.54,0:43:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.54,0:44:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.99,0:44:02.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.46,0:44:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.33,0:44:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop keep finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.21,0:44:07.26,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But he said heart again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.96,0:44:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He said heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.03,0:44:11.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And for the purchased white basket....
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.92,0:44:11.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.00,0:44:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.17,0:44:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.61,0:44:19.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It fits nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.54,0:44:20.04,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.24,0:44:21.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just how his mother wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.35,0:44:22.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,Useful for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.88,0:44:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.28,0:44:28.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not how his mother wanted it with toro as a renummeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.29,0:44:31.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's salmon and lean tuna as they usually get.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.41,0:44:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.19,0:44:39.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats the usual taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.13,0:44:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a childlike errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.63,0:44:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's remarkable that he tried so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.40,0:45:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how children run errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.58,0:45:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.37,0:45:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The store manager has never been \Nso happy in his life to sell a basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.96,0:45:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.26,0:45:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like he was about to cry during the departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.56,0:45:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(968.727,292.545)}Emotional bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.03,0:45:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.36,0:45:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,During the entire thing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.77,0:45:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tomida was crying the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.57,0:45:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(889,555)}Full of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.95,0:45:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can empathize, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.75,0:45:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.70,0:45:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(242.909,516.545)}Father of 2 sons with these ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.82,0:45:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the on-air of me crying it made me cry even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.94,0:45:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying person.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.80,0:45:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.00,0:45:36.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During Halloween the Japanese who are thought of as being shy
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.67,0:45:40.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,have started wearing clothes and parading down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.79,0:45:45.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a magical day where you get \Nthe chance to overcome shyness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.74,0:45:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010.91,142.728)}Shinyu   ●  Yuzawa city
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.28,0:45:49.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here's a household intending on having a first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.50,0:46:00.17,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(512,333.273)}Chihana\N4 years 11 months
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.02,0:46:00.17,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1117.091,342)}Momoka\N2 years 10 months
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.96,0:45:52.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister tends to get easily embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.02,0:45:55.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,except for on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.21,0:45:57.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 2 year old Momoka is always chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.74,0:46:00.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know about shyness yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.30,0:46:04.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will call over friends to their house today and have a Halloween party.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.33,0:46:09.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will hollow out the pumpkin to use it as a cheese fondue bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.89,0:46:12.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's always the brother who goes on errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.37,0:46:18.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They insist on being useful to their mom, so the mom thought of this errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.28,0:46:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo, what about milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.08,0:46:22.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the little sister Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.70,0:46:25.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Milk is needed in cheese fondue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.95,0:46:29.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momokas role in the home is to bring the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.41,0:46:32.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.08,0:46:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please buy milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.21,0:46:35.70,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to go with mama and buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.70,0:46:37.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Momoka can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.15,0:46:39.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about big sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.18,0:46:41.05,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.18,0:46:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go buy milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.19,0:46:42.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can do Momokas part.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.92,0:46:45.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will go an buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.42,0:46:50.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sis was asked to get shredded cheese and a slab of bacon
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.71,0:46:52.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and about the milk
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.73,0:46:56.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,unlike the usual one, the stronger unprocessed one will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.25,0:46:58.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mom went for a difficult request.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.82,0:47:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Difficult indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.07,0:47:01.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,Unprocessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.60,0:47:02.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.27,0:47:04.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,50 meters from the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.93,0:47:08.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mom went with the closest option because of Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.11,0:47:12.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, so Momoka is going after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.42,0:47:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.39,0:47:15.35,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Off we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.08,0:47:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.94,0:47:19.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Big sis, Momoka is now in your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.76,0:47:23.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,... then where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.16,0:47:24.28,Studio,,0,0,0,,What, what, what.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.56,0:47:25.63,Studio,,0,0,0,,Off the bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.83,0:47:28.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's going out back. That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.02,0:47:30.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In front of our film crew campout.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.27,0:47:33.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Apparently there was a shortcut through the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.42,0:47:36.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But there's an obstacle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.98,0:47:41.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This water ditch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.35,0:47:45.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem for the big sister but for Momoka it's impossible. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.27,0:47:51.89,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.89,0:47:55.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do I have to go here in order to go to the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.94,0:47:59.41,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.90,0:48:01.07,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.07,0:48:05.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momoka is already regretting that she went with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.70,0:48:09.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.32,0:48:09.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Do your best. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.29,0:48:13.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I got all dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.76,0:48:16.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momoka is pouting a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.85,0:48:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.53,0:48:23.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because the milk has to be unprocessed
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.35,0:48:27.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momoka can't, but the big sister seems able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.38,0:48:32.01,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,595)}Milk first.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.73,0:48:33.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cherfully running towards the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.67,0:48:38.17,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,595)}It's not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.02,0:48:38.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they need the unprocessed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.92,0:48:41.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momoka can't but the big sister can.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.64,0:48:42.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This one perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.17,0:48:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.66,0:48:49.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the same milk as usual. Not the unprocessed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.90,0:48:54.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And what about the grated cheese and bacon?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.68,0:48:54.54,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.32,0:48:59.21,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Momo wants to give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.21,0:49:02.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the person in charge of the milk, Momoko wants to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.38,0:49:06.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wants to feel like she's the one who purchased it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.57,0:49:14.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sister knows about the melted cheese and bacon
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.86,0:49:17.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but she's too shy to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.54,0:49:24.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's too dejected to take the shortcut on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.67,0:49:28.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's downtrodden from her embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.67,0:49:29.07,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is she embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.39,0:49:30.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,She couldn't purchase her part.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.97,0:49:32.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,She couldn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.79,0:49:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.48,0:49:39.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,591)}I could only get the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.16,0:49:39.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I was too embarrassed to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.73,0:49:41.40,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,588)}Embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.80,0:49:43.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The magic of Halloween didn't do its trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.88,0:49:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine fine. It's so close so you can go as many times as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.17,0:49:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go see the lady again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.04,0:49:52.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At first she intended to make her \Ngo on the errand in a princess dress but
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.89,0:49:55.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,because of the rain she's wearing a rain coat instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.90,0:49:59.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister will always hide behind her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.79,0:50:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay because you did your best so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.12,0:50:04.00,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:05.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momo is cool as a cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.26,0:50:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Momo, can you go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.72,0:50:07.71,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.71,0:50:08.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.56,0:50:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the usual milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.04,0:50:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this one but unprocessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.83,0:50:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask for unprocessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.93,0:50:15.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Big sis, it's impossible for Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.93,0:50:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.07,0:50:19.34,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Unprocessed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.07,0:50:19.34,Studio,,0,0,0,,Yeah unprocessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.70,0:50:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask for unprocessed milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.99,0:50:22.97,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.77,0:50:25.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,Will she go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.73,0:50:28.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Surely the big sister will worry and chase after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.75,0:50:31.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother believes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.02,0:50:36.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's going through the arcade this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.77,0:50:36.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.81,0:50:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she say "unprocessed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.11,0:50:44.48,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Please return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.48,0:50:46.80,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Please return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.80,0:50:48.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She understands returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.60,0:50:51.44,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.93,0:50:52.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,Unprosshd?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.52,0:50:53.87,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.60,0:50:54.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.66,0:50:58.48,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,592.286)}Which is unprosshd?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.42,0:50:59.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She even remembers to say unprocessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.84,0:51:02.90,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Which is unprosshd?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.23,0:51:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you always get?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.90,0:51:05.08,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.32,0:51:07.03,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,593.429)}Unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.33,0:51:08.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She thinks she's saying it right but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.60,0:51:11.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.22,0:51:11.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.62,0:51:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me the big cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.76,0:51:17.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister has still not changed her mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.69,0:51:20.93,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I was so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.93,0:51:23.00,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.87,0:51:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Too embarrased to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.03,0:51:23.60,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.60,0:51:26.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mom stops holding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.34,0:51:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't go then we won't be able to have a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.98,0:51:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cancel it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.09,0:51:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call them and say "hey, we can't do it".
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.70,0:51:39.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cancelling todays halloween party?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.27,0:51:41.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or to do the errand despite shyness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.65,0:51:43.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One of these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.52,0:51:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and look at how Momoka is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.06,0:51:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a look if she's getting the unprocessed milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.49,0:51:50.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If it's only a peek then it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.18,0:51:54.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's worried about her little sister\N so she will go for her little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.47,0:51:58.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.21,0:52:05.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.73,0:52:09.83,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,603.714)}Unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.86,0:52:08.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's still doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.48,0:52:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The one your mom asked you to buy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.22,0:52:14.08,Studio,,0,0,0,,She doesn't get unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.42,0:52:14.12,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.12,0:52:17.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now her big sister arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.45,0:52:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.89,0:52:20.14,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Unprocessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.36,0:52:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's unprocessed then it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.53,0:52:26.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She immediately understood thanks to big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.83,0:52:25.30,Studio,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.53,0:52:27.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,Thanks to her indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.15,0:52:30.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. The unprosshd one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.92,0:52:33.57,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Is this the unprosshd one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.57,0:52:37.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The lady didn't think that a 2 year old was trying to say such a difficult word.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.21,0:52:40.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.21,0:52:43.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.50,0:52:46.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And melting cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.30,0:52:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Melting cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.07,0:52:50.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She overcame her shyness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.84,0:52:54.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She only came to watch, but is she going to buy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.53,0:52:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.54,0:52:59.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is for putting on bread. It will melt but it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.73,0:52:59.50,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.13,0:53:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you make with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.25,0:53:04.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Cheese fondue.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.67,0:53:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese fondue? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.84,0:53:07.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady doesn't know such luxurious cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.75,0:53:11.21,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,598)}Round bacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.36,0:53:13.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not exactly round. It should be a slab of bacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.51,0:53:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bacon slab.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.58,0:53:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.78,0:53:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this slab? Will it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.30,0:53:23.50,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}Okay, please this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.94,0:53:23.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No, this is ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.12,0:53:24.35,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.62,0:53:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will loin ham do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.64,0:53:28.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's so embarrassed that she can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.79,0:53:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.09,0:53:32.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Whatever. She just wants to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.93,0:53:34.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,It turned into ham and cheese toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.20,0:53:37.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she was able to go to the checkout properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.94,0:53:41.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry. I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.59,0:53:42.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see. She's too shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.42,0:53:43.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can't even lift her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.74,0:53:47.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She knows that she got the wrong things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.14,0:53:48.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,She does?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.63,0:53:50.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She knows it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.53,0:53:55.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's not even holding Momoka's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.72,0:53:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no no.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.99,0:53:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.76,0:54:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.82,0:54:03.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother isn't scolding them but greeting them warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.34,0:54:06.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's no good. She won't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.83,0:54:09.42,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.35,0:54:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine because you did your best so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.57,0:54:12.67,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I will buy bacon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.65,0:54:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.67,0:54:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo will you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.62,0:54:14.40,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.40,0:54:17.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momoka will be useful again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.71,0:54:20.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Well see ya later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.54,0:54:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.11,0:54:28.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momoka is always cool as a cucumber. She can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.68,0:54:30.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,She will be soaking by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.54,0:54:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.90,0:54:32.26,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.39,0:54:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this kind of cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.79,0:54:38.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For the Halloween party this won't be enough cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.41,0:54:42.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Momoka won't understand. I better go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.12,0:54:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.15,0:54:52.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister didn't take the shortcut for her sisters sake this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.02,0:55:06.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've walked through this door so many times today.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.54,0:55:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.94,0:55:11.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't lose to your shyness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.76,0:55:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.91,0:55:14.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sorry to hassle you, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.12,0:55:21.12,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We need a bacon slab.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.12,0:55:25.04,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Where do you have bacon slabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.36,0:55:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a bacon slab?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.18,0:55:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this one from before? The big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.43,0:55:33.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the right one. No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.32,0:55:33.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.67,0:55:37.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister is finally laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.27,0:55:40.67,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This slabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.22,0:55:43.59,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,594.571)}And the cheese was wrong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.08,0:55:45.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's riding on a high.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.38,0:55:45.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,Right right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.93,0:55:48.82,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.45,0:55:48.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.95,0:55:51.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this they can make cheese fondue.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.29,0:55:54.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.07,0:55:58.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Returning the wrong things and purchasing these. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.96,0:56:01.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has overcome her shyness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.66,0:56:03.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's smiling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.91,0:56:05.48,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.88,0:56:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.48,0:56:08.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was even able to properly show gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.88,0:56:08.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.05,0:56:11.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice. A proper big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.49,0:56:15.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A face full of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.28,0:56:20.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister takes the shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.20,0:56:22.15,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.15,0:56:25.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are both walking different paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.20,0:56:30.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is wondering why they are separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.31,0:56:32.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.96,0:56:38.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Going each their own way they will still make the same memory of this errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.32,0:56:41.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I want to be helpful."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.45,0:56:45.07,Studio,,0,0,0,,She really did her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.22,0:56:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. What's with that expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.39,0:56:48.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's grinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.91,0:56:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This. This. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.46,0:56:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well carrying this heavy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.63,0:56:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.64,0:57:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. Enter. Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.24,0:57:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.37,0:57:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.66,0:57:09.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To be helpful towards your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.86,0:57:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I did try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.05,0:57:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Momo, get your thank you hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.97,0:57:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.65,0:57:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your sister did well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.65,0:57:19.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The uprocessed milk from Momoka
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.32,0:57:21.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,melted with her sister's cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.59,0:57:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.60,0:57:29.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a Halloween specialty: "Pumpkin cheese fondue".
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.72,0:57:30.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.13,0:57:33.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their friends also came while all dressed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.79,0:57:33.95,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.60,0:57:36.91,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The bacon is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.46,0:57:36.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their big brother agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.91,0:57:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She overcame and bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.81,0:57:40.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was able to help everyone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.94,0:57:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we poured all of Momo's milk into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.91,0:57:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a helpful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.90,0:57:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Also Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.00,0:57:53.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both of them love being sung their praises.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.88,0:57:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.88,0:57:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice party.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.53,0:58:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.53,0:58:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice party.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.05,0:58:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.27,0:58:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them are really well behaved.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.52,0:58:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She said unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.94,0:58:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unprosshd.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.12,0:58:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you say unprosshd in the milk aisle in can only mean unprocessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.92,0:58:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.23,0:58:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu, if you had a little sister like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.06,0:58:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(293.818,594.908)}5 year older brother and\N 4 year older sister
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.06,0:58:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I really thought that it was like my relation to my brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.15,0:58:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that the sister was without any fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.61,0:58:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,While the big sister looks out and is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.79,0:58:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks about the bigger perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.86,0:58:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.06,0:58:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(295.273,510.728)}2 year older brother
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.36,0:58:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a big brother and our grandparents really were affectionate with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.87,0:58:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They would take me out every day like department stores
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.14,0:58:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or Japanese confectionary shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.28,0:58:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's all their fault how I've turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.22,0:58:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fault? Don't you mean thanks to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.30,0:58:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.60,0:58:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.49,0:58:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking about grandchildren
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.44,0:59:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,both you, Tokoro, and Ito have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.69,0:59:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You will do anything they ask you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.59,0:59:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.59,0:59:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.10,0:59:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The same is true for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.78,0:59:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576.286)}Nothing hurts when it comes to grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.07,0:59:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what they do to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.40,0:59:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Being hit.. like...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.34,0:59:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,being stabbed with a toy sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.21,0:59:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.57,0:59:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.51,0:59:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635.636,608.182)}Miyagi ● Matsushima City
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.51,0:59:26.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sunrise in one of the three beauty spots of Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.63,0:59:30.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Matsushima where you can also see the Shiogama shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.72,0:59:33.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a tradition that has been carried on for over 1200 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.31,0:59:37.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a shrine that draws attraction from all over Touhoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.06,0:59:39.48,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's this amazing on the first day after New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.73,0:59:40.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's bustling.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.41,0:59:44.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the past, only men of the Date clan were allowed to climb this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.12,0:59:48.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is here, they will climb these stone steps as their first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.02,0:59:50.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,The steps \Nstretch far here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.61,0:59:52.08,Studio,,0,0,0,,But it's a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.49,0:59:57.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Children aged 3, 5 and 7 have come to visit on this autumn day.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.42,1:00:01.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boy who will go on an errand lives at a candy shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.27,1:00:05.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's like living in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.74,1:00:08.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To be surrounded by a ton of toys every day
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.29,1:00:11.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ramune, fugashi and dried apricot sticks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.98,1:00:11.73,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's like heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.14,1:00:14.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boy to envy is Naoki.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.30,1:00:18.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's always energetic and his favorite game is to play house.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.65,1:00:22.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one appearing here is....
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.94,1:00:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.36,1:00:26.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's his girlfriend, Seina.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.04,1:00:30.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A month older, at 3 years and 11 month old
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.15,1:00:33.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,they've known each other from birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.30,1:00:35.99,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.62,1:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go too far.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.76,1:00:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We were asked by daddy to visit the shrine and purchase a charm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.43,1:00:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.78,1:00:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of any good charms?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.88,1:00:49.55,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,To smoothen things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.78,1:00:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ah yeah what was it...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.33,1:00:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of charm is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.74,1:00:56.57,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,574)}To smoothen things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.97,1:00:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To smoothen things? Is there one like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.74,1:00:59.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The very popular charm at Shiogama shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.04,1:01:02.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A charm to smoothen things. \NCould be useful for the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.38,1:01:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A charm to smoothen things.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.51,1:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- What if you went together?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.96,1:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Will you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.75,1:01:07.72,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I could even go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.72,1:01:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No way you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.69,1:01:11.62,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.62,1:01:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are ya saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.52,1:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay but...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.59,1:01:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go along with Seina? The two of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.99,1:01:20.50,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.43,1:01:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are two charms.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.25,1:01:23.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hidden mic charms.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.68,1:01:25.39,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.02,1:01:25.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Boys prefer blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.90,1:01:28.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh!? He wants the red one?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.09,1:01:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what's on it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.64,1:01:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch yours to Seina's.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.40,1:01:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So please get along all lovey-dovey.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.40,1:01:41.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.75,1:01:44.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All lovey-dovey.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.07,1:01:47.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The soy sauce shop is at the foot of the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.27,1:01:51.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,they were asked to get round-shaped konjaku called Tama-kon.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.41,1:01:57.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then it is a 202 stairs climb up Omotesando.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.07,1:02:00.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,*It was a hill only men of the Date clan were allowed to climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.07,1:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(619.636,74.363)}Mens' climb: The steeper one. \NWomens' climb: The least steep one.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.27,1:02:02.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then they enter the grounds to purchase the charm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.67,1:02:08.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On their way back they will go down the women's climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.65,1:02:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know which hill to go up?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.52,1:02:12.72,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,The male climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.72,1:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about the return?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.29,1:02:15.57,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,The female climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.57,1:02:18.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected from a local boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.02,1:02:21.96,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I've started craving dango.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.92,1:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.96,1:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you then go and buy some?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.94,1:02:24.16,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.16,1:02:28.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This adds a new errand. Dango, enough for 5.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.63,1:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.52,1:02:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will command the male climb?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.87,1:02:31.85,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Seina.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.87,1:02:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seina will command the steep climb?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.85,1:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will command the female climb?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.89,1:02:35.97,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(366.857,598)}I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.59,1:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao will? Isn't it reversed?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.72,1:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Commanding officers do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.63,1:02:41.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hoping to get along. Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.83,1:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.23,1:02:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We will rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.91,1:03:15.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The long-established soy sauce shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.11,1:03:17.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? The bamboo blinds are down.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.90,1:03:19.17,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Here perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.17,1:03:20.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is it locked?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.47,1:03:21.97,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, must be closed today.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.97,1:03:23.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's before the opening hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.37,1:03:28.09,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,They haven't opened? Let's tell mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.01,1:03:28.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Too early.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.19,1:03:31.63,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Nao, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.85,1:03:34.10,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Don't run.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.61,1:03:34.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they came all the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.10,1:03:37.60,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, we must get the dango first.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.69,1:03:41.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They're running back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.92,1:03:45.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will they have enough stamina for the climb?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.24,1:03:50.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Right at that moment the shop is opening up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.46,1:03:51.73,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's good that they went back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.73,1:03:53.28,Studio,,0,0,0,,They were early.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.38,1:03:53.60,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's opening now?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.60,1:03:56.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Phew, we made it" the camera man thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.55,1:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.12,1:03:59.99,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I want that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.99,1:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Round konjyaku?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.09,1:04:02.33,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,How many do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.33,1:04:04.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The always reliable Seina.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.76,1:04:06.83,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,3 please.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.40,1:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,3? Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.83,1:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want it in a bag?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.03,1:04:10.32,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.32,1:04:11.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So adult-like.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.47,1:04:12.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.44,1:04:16.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Tama-kon steeped in soy sauce are only sold on holidays.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.66,1:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.39,1:04:20.93,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.33,1:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.20,1:04:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take the 500 yen. Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.67,1:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's cold outside
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.78,1:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,please have one each.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.04,1:04:33.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The traditional preparation of konjac that has been steeped in soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.64,1:04:36.68,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,585.429)}Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.46,1:04:37.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.63,1:04:42.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Leaving the soy sauce shop they have a steep climb ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.37,1:04:46.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Kids love to run.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.59,1:04:51.31,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.84,1:04:51.31,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.31,1:04:53.51,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,The dango shop is next.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.01,1:04:53.51,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.51,1:04:55.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the charm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.55,1:04:57.81,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.81,1:04:59.35,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,202 steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.35,1:05:00.75,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,202 steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.75,1:05:03.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just as they said. It's 202 steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.44,1:05:06.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not an easy climb even for adults.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.71,1:05:11.23,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.23,1:05:12.50,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.50,1:05:14.60,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Please hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.60,1:05:15.52,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.65,1:05:17.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's making {\i1}her{\i0} carry it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.73,1:05:18.33,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I have no power.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.33,1:05:19.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about Seina?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.95,1:05:20.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,And she's the girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.29,1:05:22.29,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I do have power.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.25,1:05:22.29,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Where is the power?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.29,1:05:24.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nao is losing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.34,1:05:26.79,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's a guarding lion-dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.79,1:05:28.03,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Guarding lion-dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.03,1:05:29.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he's still buzzing full of words.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.81,1:05:32.28,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's a guarding lion-dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.56,1:05:33.12,Studio,,0,0,0,,He knows a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.33,1:05:35.44,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Hurry, let's go up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.44,1:05:37.04,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,A guarding lion-dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.04,1:05:39.12,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Next let's go this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.12,1:05:40.67,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's easier to go this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.67,1:05:41.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.74,1:05:44.23,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I will climb this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.23,1:05:45.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's smarter the other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.50,1:05:49.23,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's easier this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.65,1:05:51.43,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's easy, see!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.67,1:05:52.30,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's not easier.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.73,1:05:56.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nao is climbing the area where people stand to view the portable shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.69,1:06:00.71,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm full of vigor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.19,1:06:00.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,Tough!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.86,1:06:03.41,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.41,1:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.93,1:06:07.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina is climbing the stairs
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.97,1:06:11.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,while Nao is climbing the area where people stand to view the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.64,1:06:13.47,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm full of vigor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.87,1:06:17.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 202 step climb to Shiogama shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.56,1:06:20.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It would even exhaust adults.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.15,1:06:22.63,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Wait. Don't leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.63,1:06:23.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.58,1:06:26.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina also ended up giong that way?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.97,1:06:27.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.45,1:06:30.39,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Today you win, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.39,1:06:32.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.93,1:06:35.55,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's a horse!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.55,1:06:37.41,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.41,1:06:38.46,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's a horse!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.46,1:06:39.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A horse is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.55,1:06:41.22,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's a cow, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.22,1:06:42.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was a cow.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.72,1:06:44.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,A cow.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.05,1:06:47.06,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we can get a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.31,1:06:51.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wonder if Seina understood Nao's wish to get one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.68,1:06:54.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.82,1:06:57.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nao also got one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.78,1:06:57.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.99,1:07:01.00,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yellow.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.02,1:07:03.84,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I wanted a pink one.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.84,1:07:05.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go get one yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.24,1:07:09.91,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We have to put money in, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.96,1:07:11.75,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,591.143)}Yes, money.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.75,1:07:11.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's saisen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.75,1:07:14.08,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We give all of our money, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.08,1:07:14.98,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.33,1:07:17.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina puts 500 yen in.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.45,1:07:19.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Nao?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.54,1:07:22.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.13,1:07:24.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.83,1:07:26.43,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It doesn't ring...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.43,1:07:27.25,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.16,1:07:29.75,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It won't ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.98,1:07:30.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have the power.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.13,1:07:31.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.15,1:07:34.30,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Ring ring
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.30,1:07:36.17,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Ring ring ring
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.17,1:07:37.61,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Nao, it rang.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.61,1:07:38.94,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.28,1:07:40.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.66,1:07:41.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.56,1:07:43.81,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Next is the charm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.10,1:07:45.23,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.23,1:07:46.62,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's get one.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.62,1:07:48.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will buy a charm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.55,1:07:53.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a grand atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.16,1:07:56.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.13,1:07:58.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.58,1:08:00.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To be able to honor your ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.08,1:08:02.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thinking that they might stand by and watch...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.62,1:08:04.50,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.50,1:08:06.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They weren't even watching it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.13,1:08:06.54,Studio,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.30,1:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.60,1:08:10.87,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,To smoothen things.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.87,1:08:11.96,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.96,1:08:13.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,They can read?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.16,1:08:13.34,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's buy this.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.34,1:08:16.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina bought the charm to smoothen things.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.39,1:08:26.04,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,There are so many cute girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.54,1:08:28.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's a boy after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.48,1:08:34.26,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I wanted a pink one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.35,1:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still harping on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.90,1:08:38.18,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Nao, please don't run, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.18,1:08:40.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina is getting tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.00,1:08:41.37,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Dango shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.37,1:08:43.51,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.51,1:08:47.04,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,You were told not to run, weren't you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.04,1:08:48.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's being told so many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.24,1:08:50.68,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Nao, you will trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.73,1:08:51.48,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.48,1:08:53.55,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.70,1:08:54.03,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's sprinting.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.55,1:08:54.98,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.98,1:08:57.82,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yay, so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.17,1:08:59.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,The adults can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.84,1:08:59.52,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,What about the dango?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.52,1:09:00.72,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.72,1:09:02.56,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Dango.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.56,1:09:05.03,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,There's so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.16,1:09:05.03,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Won't you purchase dango?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.03,1:09:07.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They sell the masks at your home, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.83,1:09:09.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They were asked to get dango for 5 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.75,1:09:12.80,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Dango, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.17,1:09:12.80,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Dango, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.24,1:09:15.52,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,591.143)}With this kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.37,1:09:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You were given this much money?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.14,1:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.14,1:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,3 boxes? 2 boxes?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.74,1:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Or 5?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.28,1:09:24.41,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,598)}Yep, 5 boxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.81,1:09:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't 5 be a wee too heavy to carry?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.80,1:09:27.23,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,596.857)}We can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.67,1:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.60,1:09:30.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Won't 5 be a bit too heavy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.77,1:09:32.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina is worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.84,1:09:38.43,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We will eat for two.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.43,1:09:40.20,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,And then we bring it to our mamas.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.20,1:09:41.53,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.03,1:09:42.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.37,1:09:44.43,Studio,,0,0,0,,They were planning to eat them all there?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.25,1:09:48.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they both eat and take 3 back with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.40,1:09:49.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.92,1:09:50.21,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.21,1:09:53.24,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We thought of a nice thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.72,1:09:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What nice thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.24,1:09:55.04,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,If we eat for two {\alphaFF}and for out moms...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.04,1:09:57.04,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,If we eat for two and for out moms...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.04,1:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A present?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.55,1:09:58.30,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.30,1:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You will only eat your portion. Got ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.72,1:10:05.30,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.81,1:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For mama and papa, right? I'm writing\N a letter to them so please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.24,1:10:12.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's writing a receipt.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.26,1:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This old lady will hold them for you so please give them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.68,1:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,since you plan on eating dango first.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.57,1:10:24.92,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,If the wind blows hard they will fly away.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.92,1:10:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Which is why this old lady will hold them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.23,1:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.05,1:10:32.15,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,594.571)}But what if you forget them?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.71,1:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.15,1:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's afraid she will keep them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.95,1:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your spare change cause you gave me 3000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.20,1:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them you purchased 5.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.36,1:10:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And the two of you will eat your part, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.29,1:10:42.56,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.56,1:10:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a freebie for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.44,1:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are such good kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.25,1:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who understood it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.23,1:10:49.90,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,We did!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.90,1:10:51.43,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I love this dango.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.43,1:10:53.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much old lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.67,1:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.99,1:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What about saying grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.32,1:10:59.34,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.07,1:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.34,1:11:01.59,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.06,1:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.59,1:11:04.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you the two of them are enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.15,1:11:05.65,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.80,1:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Two warm teas, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.82,1:11:11.52,Studio,,0,0,0,,He loves dango.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.71,1:11:14.86,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Um, how delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.39,1:11:16.49,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama is waiting...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.49,1:11:20.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like the old lady the dango has a kind taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.55,1:11:23.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.03,1:11:25.97,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Is this free service?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.18,1:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.42,1:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.91,1:11:34.48,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.17,1:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.48,1:11:37.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They properly said "thanks for the meal".
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.78,1:11:41.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since the dango they ate were freebies they are bringing 5 back.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.62,1:11:43.57,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.87,1:11:43.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.57,1:11:45.67,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,They have cotton candy and masks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.67,1:11:49.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't they sell lots of masks at the shop where Nao lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.48,1:11:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.35,1:11:55.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The balloons!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.83,1:11:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This old lady forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.82,1:11:58.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,So close.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.43,1:11:59.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,Just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.28,1:11:59.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,They did forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.59,1:12:04.17,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I can only hold 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.14,1:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold 1 and she will hold 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.17,1:12:08.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Glad she didn't have to chase them down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.79,1:12:08.86,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.86,1:12:11.11,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,How many yen are these?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.11,1:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One is 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.58,1:12:14.48,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I will get one for 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.48,1:12:16.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite them selling so many at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.30,1:12:19.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's still tempting.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.85,1:12:22.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not the blue, he likes the red one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.73,1:12:25.04,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I will get this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.28,1:12:27.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have those at home too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.20,1:12:30.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,Must be different to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.90,1:12:34.40,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's so loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.54,1:12:38.21,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.60,1:12:45.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the smaller slope of higashisando.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.43,1:12:46.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,Please go slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.33,1:12:48.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameramen are tired too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.67,1:12:53.46,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.46,1:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.31,1:12:56.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He called out to the cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.81,1:12:59.50,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,This one is so loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.50,1:13:01.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nice chance. Make use of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.35,1:13:06.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile the cameramen are running ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.50,1:13:09.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,This must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.82,1:13:11.82,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.97,1:13:13.01,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.99,1:13:16.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We were able to get a shot from the front.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.33,1:13:18.50,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Nao, you might trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.87,1:13:22.17,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Our mamas must be worrying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.89,1:13:29.64,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Errand errand how fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.74,1:13:32.50,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,A dango order coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.50,1:13:34.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Shiro from next door.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.95,1:13:38.77,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Shiro you can't eat the dango.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.62,1:13:41.34,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's not even saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.69,1:13:43.32,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Go... errand...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.32,1:13:45.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've arrived home.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.38,1:13:48.84,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm tired by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.41,1:13:48.84,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.03,1:13:55.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They didn't fall once and now that they are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.64,1:13:58.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh no, the tama-kons.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.67,1:14:01.52,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,The tama-kons...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.29,1:14:02.79,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's fine if they just wash it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.86,1:14:07.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mothers, the two of them did it all the way without any hiccups.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.53,1:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wash and eat them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.85,1:14:14.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since the soy sauce has permeated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.80,1:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you buy a charm?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.41,1:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this balloon?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.22,1:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.98,1:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.11,1:14:23.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.00,1:14:24.30,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's eat them together!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.30,1:14:26.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nao is the one who settled things.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.65,1:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.72,1:14:32.09,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I ate one of these.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.09,1:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you eat dango there?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.41,1:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. How unfair.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.36,1:14:40.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They went on their first errand in 2008.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.85,1:14:43.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,9 years later
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.17,1:14:44.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from the errand when they were 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.88,1:14:48.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shiogama was hit by the Great East Japan Earthquake
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.09,1:14:51.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,People had to evacuate to the hilltop shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.22,1:14:55.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina and her family moved to Kanagawa prefecture after the earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.98,1:14:59.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In all those years it's the first time that she has returned.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.38,1:15:05.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First year students of junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.29,1:15:05.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.60,1:15:05.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,They've become so big.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.84,1:15:07.39,Studio,,0,0,0,,They still get along.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.96,1:15:11.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It rings this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.80,1:15:17.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their moms are best friends so they'll always have a connection.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.54,1:15:22.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they've come all this way they better get a charm to smoothen things.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.57,1:15:24.81,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.34,1:15:30.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As junior high students what do they wish will go well?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.56,1:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wish will go well?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.62,1:15:34.33,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Club activity and study.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.33,1:15:35.32,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Study?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.32,1:15:36.77,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Studying doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.77,1:15:40.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's he saying? Actually Nao is performing well in his studies.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.27,1:15:43.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's completely into tennis after school.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.50,1:15:52.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Please, only edit in the good parts" he told us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.89,1:15:57.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Something he's more into is...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.02,1:16:00.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He wants to become a pâtisserie when he grows up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.06,1:16:06.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once he heard that Seina was coming he's been making cakes since morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.87,1:16:12.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With various decorations.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.22,1:16:13.37,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.37,1:16:16.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wonder which one is for Seina.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.04,1:16:17.08,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.08,1:16:19.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? One of them is special.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.80,1:16:24.90,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,This one is for Seina.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.90,1:16:28.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's actually Seina's birthday tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.39,1:16:32.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Surprising her with two gifts, eh? I see...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.91,1:16:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.79,1:16:37.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seina is in the brass-band club.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.01,1:16:39.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's playing the biggest instrument: The tuba.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.05,1:16:40.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.22,1:16:43.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After trying out several students she was able to play it best.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.22,1:16:46.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's been playing since junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.74,1:16:49.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Before that was karate, gymnastics, swimming.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.54,1:16:54.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An instrument that requires force and lung capacity. A true match for Seina.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.58,1:16:59.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To carry a 10 kilo tuba lightly
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.44,1:17:01.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.35,1:17:04.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and to make it look fun during performances.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.72,1:17:08.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's practicing that right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.43,1:17:14.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During the earthquake, it caused a tsunami so great...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.03,1:17:16.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that it carried tour boats, docked in the marina, onto land.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.10,1:17:19.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two don't bring those times up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.27,1:17:23.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dango shop used to be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.51,1:17:24.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.56,1:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure grew up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.65,1:17:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady has also become quite old.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.25,1:17:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.90,1:17:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How has everything been?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.40,1:17:34.20,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.67,1:17:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been such a long time since you tried my oden.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.17,1:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,These oden will be a freebie.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.34,1:17:41.39,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,617.429)}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.51,1:17:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming and visiting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.98,1:17:47.15,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I've made these.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.15,1:17:49.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He decided they will eat them at the dango shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.59,1:17:50.85,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.85,1:17:53.12,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Please eat the one you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.79,1:17:57.21,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they taste good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.33,1:17:58.76,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Incredibly delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.00,1:18:02.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He won't give her the birthday special?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.88,1:18:03.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,Huh. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.77,1:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.23,1:18:07.30,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I forgot to bring it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.30,1:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.69,1:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It finally came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.96,1:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.06,1:18:14.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. And he woke up early because of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.24,1:18:16.95,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,When we get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.15,1:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get back?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.31,1:18:19.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Naoki who hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.30,1:18:21.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,What was he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.83,1:18:21.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,At such an important time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.12,1:18:23.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His store managed to be spared, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.60,1:18:28.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the seawater came up to waist height and many of the shops were severely damaged.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.21,1:18:30.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This. This.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.18,1:18:31.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The important thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.15,1:18:38.30,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's a bit early but happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.67,1:18:38.30,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.30,1:18:41.20,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's made from choco-chip banana.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.20,1:18:43.21,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.21,1:18:45.12,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Why are you speaking so formal?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.12,1:18:48.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This awkward distance is normal for first year junior high students.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.61,1:18:50.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.20,1:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I got really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.32,1:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Naoki all boys that age when they get excited they run around a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.08,1:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She told him: "Don't run!"
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.79,1:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so energetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.56,1:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apropos Miyagi Prefecture, Sandwich Man you...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.05,1:19:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's my home area.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.97,1:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I often go to Shiogama.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.05,1:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, your home area.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.23,1:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bring up some memories?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.17,1:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in kindergarten and living in Ishinomaki
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.32,1:19:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a butcher not close by.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.75,1:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to go get 500 g. minced meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.31,1:19:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I went by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.52,1:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I arrived at the butcher
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.20,1:19:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said: "Please give me 500 g. of muscle."
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.16,1:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to go back and ask again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.46,1:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the way back there was a big street that I had to cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.45,1:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I put my hand up to cross a taxi stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.59,1:19:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When a child rasies their hands
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.84,1:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not to hail a ride.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.97,1:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it vividly.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.38,1:19:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about the chance\N if your kid could go on an errand?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.73,1:20:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to let them but I'm also afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.83,1:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would probably dress up like the staff here and follow him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.94,1:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the parents must be so worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.66,1:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.66,1:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But there will be a day when they\N have to be allowed out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.20,1:20:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A father who has made this decision is here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.95,1:20:20.73,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660.364,506.364)}Special Guest will appear
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.95,1:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's welcome him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.74,1:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, please enter this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.04,1:20:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.66,1:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro-boxing's former WBC World Bantamweight Champion
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.87,1:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.99,1:20:40.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka papa who was the strongest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.39,1:20:42.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will send his children on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.74,1:20:47.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.91,1:20:49.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's different from inside of the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.77,1:20:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.62,1:20:52.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's riddled with anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.70,1:20:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.07,1:21:18.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You will continue to be moved.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.81,1:21:22.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A first errand in the harsh nature of Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.16,1:21:26.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A girl who gives it her all even in the face of challenges.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.30,1:21:29.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A whirlwind of emotions from the studio!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.42,1:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.56,1:21:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the former WBC bantamweight world champion: Yamanaka Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.52,1:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.18,1:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.29,1:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You made your young go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.94,1:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.66,1:21:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.96,1:21:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.53,1:21:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and I were in high spirits...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.93,1:21:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We were however...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.13,1:21:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,just before the shooting
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.65,1:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we were so anxious.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.95,1:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.21,1:22:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,4 days in advance we thought "it might not be possible".
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.89,1:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let's not do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.11,1:22:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have the confidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.62,1:22:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you haven't seen the footage, have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.60,1:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.72,1:22:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.61,1:22:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(221.091,515.091)}Anxious
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.12,1:22:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please face camera 2 and
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.53,1:22:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,introduce the clip, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.06,1:22:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,While my heart is beating fast, please enjoy this clip.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.00,1:22:37.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pro-boxer Yamanaka Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.73,1:22:46.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,famously nicknamed "God's Left".
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.08,1:22:51.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He defended the world title 12 times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.69,1:22:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The "God's Left" is strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.24,1:23:00.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For 5 years and 9 months he didn't lose once.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.01,1:23:01.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For such a man...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.91,1:23:05.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His first son was born merely 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.67,1:23:20.22,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(149.818,484.546)}Gousuke
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.89,1:23:17.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When Gousuke was born
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.46,1:23:20.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,his father was already a world champion.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.17,1:23:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.64,1:23:29.82,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1154.909,490.364)}Ririno
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.27,1:23:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning and being able to hold my kids in the ring gives me great joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.37,1:23:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd still like to continue with one or more of these.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.78,1:23:32.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.43,1:23:34.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papa continued to win.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.81,1:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play when we get home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.72,1:23:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.00,1:23:40.00,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.00,1:23:41.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.55,1:23:45.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They grew outside of the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.26,1:23:47.51,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Congratulations papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.51,1:23:50.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While defending his championship for 12 consecutive times.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.28,1:23:54.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke became 4 years and 4 months old.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.63,1:23:58.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then during August last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.32,1:24:03.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where he had to defend the title for the 13th time.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.79,1:24:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"God's Left" Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.26,1:24:11.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They had come to support outside of the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.07,1:24:13.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke and Ririno.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.20,1:24:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, round 4.... Hard left!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.51,1:24:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Left! He's backing up!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.36,1:24:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The champion is backing up!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.26,1:24:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this!? My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.76,1:24:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I say? Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.28,1:24:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep swinging!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.73,1:24:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The champion swings back!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.53,1:24:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The towel is thrown!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.40,1:24:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My God! Yamanaka Shinsuke...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.82,1:24:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,on the verge of a Japanese record...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.86,1:24:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,loses by TKO!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.68,1:24:40.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papa lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.98,1:24:46.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the first time seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.89,1:24:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory of God's Left will never be lost on fans.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.49,1:24:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This can never be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.16,1:24:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiin-suke! Shiin-suke!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.26,1:24:58.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the first time experiencing the hardships of a loss since his birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.93,1:25:02.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The same as dad, no no, even more so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.55,1:25:03.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.87,1:25:06.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he decided that he would fight along with papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.30,1:25:09.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The gong in Goutske's heart rang that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.63,1:25:11.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the match.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.68,1:25:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Q: What will you do next?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.90,1:25:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't thought about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.76,1:25:28.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Boxer Yamanaka began to avoid the media.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.24,1:25:32.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When he said he had lost, his son responded:
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.08,1:25:34.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"But papa did his best 12 times".
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.22,1:25:36.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke consoled him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.84,1:25:40.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 months after that match.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.31,1:25:43.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The staff of "My First Errand"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.18,1:25:46.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,came to meet Yamanaka in his training room.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.66,1:25:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.16,1:25:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.00,1:25:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,May I intrude?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.38,1:25:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.02,1:25:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you lost, I think Gousuke
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.09,1:26:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,feels the same amount of hardships over it as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.73,1:26:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He suddenly said:
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.85,1:26:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, next time I think you will win.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.94,1:26:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That rang in my ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.39,1:26:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Those words sound great.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.25,1:26:24.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The kids want one more time
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.25,1:26:26.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to be taken to that place again.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.67,1:26:31.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka finally made the decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.56,1:26:35.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka held a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.28,1:26:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that you will continue being active?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.42,1:26:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.52,1:26:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.73,1:26:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it to be thought that Yamanaka
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.89,1:26:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,still packs a punch with his left.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.49,1:26:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to win.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.69,1:26:54.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was his kids that made him go back to the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.33,1:26:58.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as a thanks he wants to bring his kids back to the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.53,1:27:01.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The thing that Yamanaka thought of
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.82,1:27:05.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is a first errand
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.07,1:27:07.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that he will have both of his children go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.41,1:27:12.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ririno is a sweetheart who leaves everything to her big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.30,1:27:17.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She uses her tears to get what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.50,1:27:22.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke has a sense of justice but he gets distracted sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.99,1:27:25.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The day before the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.83,1:27:28.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The couple pay a visit to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.20,1:27:37.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He always comes to pray before his match.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.07,1:27:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For my childrens first errand
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.53,1:27:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they make it out safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.06,1:27:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.18,1:27:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.65,1:27:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.07,1:27:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will feel good in the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.54,1:27:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.39,1:27:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like with boxing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.56,1:28:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Errands are like that too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.65,1:28:04.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now it's finally the day of the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.92,1:28:07.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka papa brought up the topic.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.80,1:28:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you go buy... get this fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.14,1:28:11.81,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.34,1:28:11.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.17,1:28:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go go!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.22,1:28:14.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Oh-!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.61,1:28:16.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the errand has started.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.54,1:28:18.38,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,571.714)}Ey ey oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.48,1:28:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.68,1:28:21.18,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.91,1:28:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. For real.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.18,1:28:22.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.93,1:28:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go for a run.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.40,1:28:25.19,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.69,1:28:26.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.96,1:28:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.97,1:28:28.79,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.89,1:28:32.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father, that's the eye of a champion.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.43,1:28:33.46,Studio,,0,0,0,,That face reveals worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.61,1:28:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Too worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.35,1:28:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.26,1:28:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I made that expression?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.03,1:28:42.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not only Yamanaka papa who has to do their best.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.45,1:28:44.67,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's best to do you best.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.67,1:28:47.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Exerting herself in the harsh nature of Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.29,1:28:49.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even the studio is moved to tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.43,1:28:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.30,1:28:59.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The errand that the father asked them to go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.19,1:29:03.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To get the broken scale fixed by a repair shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.39,1:29:07.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The scale is in Gousuke's backpack.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.38,1:29:09.40,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Many bicycles are coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.05,1:29:11.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Two of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.53,1:29:12.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,Responsible big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.54,1:29:15.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is able to do the traffic safety check.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.84,1:29:18.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Looking right, then left
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.24,1:29:21.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,even though they get confused which is which.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.53,1:29:21.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,That happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.11,1:29:23.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's fine today. They didn't make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.66,1:29:26.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I've practiced so many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.08,1:29:28.88,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I probably got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.48,1:29:28.88,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.88,1:29:32.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've walked this path many times with your mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.99,1:29:33.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,What great siblings.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.89,1:29:35.72,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fine, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.87,1:29:35.72,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.79,1:29:39.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And in no time they've arrived at the big street.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.89,1:29:44.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Checking right and left and...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.60,1:29:48.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,go. No need to worry daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.50,1:29:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.97,1:29:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.67,1:29:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they do it right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.11,1:29:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They did. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.41,1:29:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.76,1:29:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just full of wondering
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.48,1:30:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if I forgot to teach it to them properly. \NIf I forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.32,1:30:05.79,Studio,,0,0,0,,But it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.09,1:30:08.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Forgetting the father who is worrying by himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.02,1:30:10.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them are proceeding on their route.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.99,1:30:14.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You are noisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.88,1:30:14.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.99,1:30:18.70,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hey, Riri. Behave!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.13,1:30:23.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Riri always ends up crying when the two of them are fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.20,1:30:25.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she won't cry today.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.46,1:30:26.83,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's holding it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.22,1:30:30.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because her charm says: "Ririno won't cry!!"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.53,1:30:36.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's looking at it and deciding not to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.20,1:30:40.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On her brothers' it says: "You are strong"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.46,1:30:42.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So he's not just about arriving.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.53,1:30:44.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,664.286)}Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.96,1:30:47.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He makes sure to bring his sister with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.41,1:30:47.23,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.72,1:30:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.80,1:30:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go work.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.72,1:30:55.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Running is his job.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.54,1:30:59.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To become a champion again
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.99,1:31:02.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he needs to redo his training.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.63,1:31:06.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh, they made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.92,1:31:08.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are crossing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.10,1:31:10.64,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.64,1:31:12.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's not crossing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.14,1:31:15.24,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's there. Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.24,1:31:18.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There is another crossing ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.63,1:31:20.46,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.46,1:31:23.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,From the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.31,1:31:25.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are several crossings.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.25,1:31:28.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their mother has showed them various crossings.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.17,1:31:30.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Gousuke doesn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.79,1:31:32.59,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.59,1:31:34.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's green.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.19,1:31:37.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But they are crossing at just the right one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.31,1:31:43.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite the big brother always running ahead...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.75,1:31:45.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,not today.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.67,1:31:48.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's why Ririno won't cry today either.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.37,1:31:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fathom it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.19,1:31:51.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.38,1:31:56.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the shopping street from the supporting hometown of Yamanaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.15,1:32:00.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is the shopping street.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.10,1:32:01.74,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.64,1:32:01.74,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.64,1:32:06.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's a small crying girl walking in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.23,1:32:09.48,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Really resembles Riri.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.70,1:32:13.92,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Really resembles Riri.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.92,1:32:16.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Though she usually cries she won't today.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.92,1:32:18.62,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Bakery.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.62,1:32:22.12,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,601.429)}Uuh, smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.54,1:32:24.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They usually drop by but not today.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.16,1:32:26.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Don't kid around.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.11,1:32:28.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because today is...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.96,1:32:32.55,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,593.429)}Going on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.90,1:32:33.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,their first errand, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.33,1:32:35.65,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.84,1:32:38.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Denka Land.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.94,1:32:41.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've arrived at the electronics store.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.91,1:32:45.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman is waiting inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.35,1:32:49.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papa's picture is on display.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.73,1:32:50.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.85,1:32:52.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For real. It's papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.17,1:32:55.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.36,1:32:55.89,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.46,1:32:59.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the continued support.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.39,1:33:02.13,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the continued support.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.48,1:33:02.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.66,1:33:04.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.68,1:33:06.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the greetings they take out the scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.05,1:33:07.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.70,1:33:07.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is it called?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.69,1:33:11.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This scale is broken so please repair it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.42,1:33:12.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,He carried this heavy thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.07,1:33:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Repair?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.99,1:33:15.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes. He was able to say it properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.26,1:33:16.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.43,1:33:18.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can it be fixed easily?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.73,1:33:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the battery is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.03,1:33:23.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Battery?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.63,1:33:24.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,The battery is missing?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.54,1:33:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there is no battery I will put one in.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.71,1:33:29.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So it was just missing a battery?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.91,1:33:32.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So there was no need to bring it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.64,1:33:34.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.96,1:33:34.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.63,1:33:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, try to step on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.23,1:33:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.64,1:33:42.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. It was the battery.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.20,1:33:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,50 yen, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.64,1:33:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa is being shown.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.23,1:33:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this is not from the other day?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.29,1:33:50.70,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.01,1:33:50.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.70,1:33:52.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.01,1:33:54.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's from his winning match.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.80,1:33:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gouchan, where's papa today?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.77,1:33:59.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I was asked to go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.84,1:33:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you were asked to go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.85,1:34:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Remarkable the two of you came.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.07,1:34:02.16,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.16,1:34:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He will have another match, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.83,1:34:06.66,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued support.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.66,1:34:10.10,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued support.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.00,1:34:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the grateful ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.10,1:34:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope he does his best.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.28,1:34:11.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.28,1:34:11.85,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.85,1:34:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gouchan, hope you also support him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.08,1:34:14.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.22,1:34:16.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When it comes to daddy's matches
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.15,1:34:17.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he comes to watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.00,1:34:34.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It has been repaired
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.57,1:34:35.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and they did the greetings
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.96,1:34:39.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and they paid the bill. \NThe did everything perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.91,1:34:43.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that time the father is...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.40,1:34:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.40,1:34:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1063.273,321.637)}Phoning\N his\N wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.62,1:34:47.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's fidgeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.37,1:34:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get home
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.99,1:34:53.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's rummaging around.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.52,1:34:54.74,RedFill,,0,0,0,,Do it properly!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.74,1:34:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.34,1:34:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about how to set it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.76,1:35:01.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's planning to put them on a different errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.32,1:35:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,200 g. of tenderloin and some shoulder roast?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.14,1:35:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.31,1:35:11.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While he's planning that the kids are coming home.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.44,1:35:13.28,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We are almost back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.33,1:35:16.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are already at their limits.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.05,1:35:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the tenderloin...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.93,1:35:20.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's still contemplating.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.55,1:35:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a decision!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.59,1:35:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to include this?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.40,1:35:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.24,1:35:27.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.17,1:35:28.46,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are already in.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.76,1:35:31.05,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.54,1:35:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.05,1:35:34.00,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa, we are home.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.18,1:35:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.00,1:35:34.78,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.05,1:35:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.92,1:35:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.65,1:35:37.75,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.75,1:35:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.52,1:35:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.71,1:35:44.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father is in utter disbelief.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.31,1:35:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.09,1:35:48.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The scale is broken
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.13,1:35:49.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,please repair it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.33,1:35:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.33,1:35:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.47,1:35:52.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can go on errands now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.78,1:35:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.75,1:35:56.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright, check the scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.24,1:35:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it turn on?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.37,1:35:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it connected?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.54,1:36:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now papa can continue to do his best.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.04,1:36:05.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papa weighs himself 4 times a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.95,1:36:07.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,61.9
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.70,1:36:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.90,1:36:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.15,1:36:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For when mama comes home
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.12,1:36:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,let's make fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.72,1:36:17.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is round 2 of the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.98,1:36:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.34,1:36:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no spring onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.51,1:36:21.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,Will it be alright, papa?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.98,1:36:24.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And we also don't have rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.35,1:36:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.93,1:36:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have rice and eggs but
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.39,1:36:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have spring onion and \Nwithout it we can't make fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.29,1:36:33.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.07,1:36:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring onions and
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.43,1:36:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to make papa stronger
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.71,1:36:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,meat is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.90,1:36:40.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To become stronger?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.48,1:36:41.87,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.87,1:36:43.52,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.52,1:36:44.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The brother can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.97,1:36:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.55,1:36:49.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In round 2 he has to pay attention to Ririno.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.47,1:36:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,About the spring onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.08,1:36:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The spring onion is Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.56,1:36:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.61,1:37:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Ririno's responsibility will be
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.33,1:37:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the tenderloin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.34,1:37:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.92,1:37:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing both of you like
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.59,1:37:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder roast.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.52,1:37:07.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Shoulder roast?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.81,1:37:10.09,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Meat from the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.09,1:37:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, also get the meat from the shoulder roast.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.31,1:37:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.12,1:37:15.78,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.78,1:37:19.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,593.429)}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.39,1:37:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright what should you say when you arrive at Takagi Meats?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.22,1:37:22.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The worried father is double-checking.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.49,1:37:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gousuke, do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.43,1:37:31.42,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin and shoulder roast.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.42,1:37:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the shoulder roast?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.77,1:37:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,200 grams.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.27,1:37:36.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected from Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.97,1:37:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If Riri doesn't remember
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.96,1:37:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gousuke will give a hint to Riri.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.54,1:37:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.76,1:37:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By tapping her shoulders etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.01,1:37:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And saying "tend.."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.65,1:37:49.38,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.38,1:37:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like saying the "tend" in "tenderloin".
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.75,1:37:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying the "tend" of "tenderloin".
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.12,1:37:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say that then Riri might remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.71,1:37:57.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now it's practice time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.91,1:38:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When you arrive at Takagi Meats.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.56,1:38:01.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Spring onion, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.73,1:38:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Also have to get onions.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.86,1:38:03.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.61,1:38:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Riri what will you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.57,1:38:07.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,"Tend" "Tend".
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.57,1:38:09.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin please.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.57,1:38:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And what else?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.54,1:38:13.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,Tapping her shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.58,1:38:16.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Shoulder roast.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.81,1:38:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right right. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.51,1:38:19.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.84,1:38:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can they do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.56,1:38:24.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad did perfect training for the second round.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.49,1:38:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's scary. One more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.30,1:38:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.76,1:38:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you buy, Gousuke?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.51,1:38:31.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Spring onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.69,1:38:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And Riri?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.30,1:38:35.60,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin and
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.23,1:38:38.35,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,aaaaand...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.65,1:38:40.07,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Shoulder roast.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.07,1:38:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.79,1:38:41.80,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.80,1:38:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.69,1:38:44.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yet again.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.41,1:38:45.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,How many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.29,1:38:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.11,1:38:48.54,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Eeh...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.54,1:38:49.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And how ever many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.78,1:38:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.71,1:38:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.28,1:38:53.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Eeh.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.68,1:38:56.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has knocked them out. What a champion.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.75,1:38:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.45,1:38:59.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We already got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.39,1:38:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.59,1:39:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel like doing your best?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.30,1:39:01.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,He wants perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.11,1:39:03.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because of his anxiety he allows no slip-ups.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.52,1:39:05.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is how a world's best does it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.98,1:39:07.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright, we are heading off.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.81,1:39:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of all the cars and bicycles.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.87,1:39:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Riri, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.47,1:39:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.09,1:39:16.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's still doing it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.62,1:39:17.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.64,1:39:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just go then.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.76,1:39:21.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Shoulder roast.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.04,1:39:21.54,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is the 15th time.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.57,1:39:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.58,1:39:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.64,1:39:24.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He finally said okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.60,1:39:27.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.21,1:39:28.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,Believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.37,1:39:29.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.37,1:39:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.92,1:39:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.27,1:39:34.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've finally been allowed to depart.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.14,1:39:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of the cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.53,1:39:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And bicycles.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.33,1:39:41.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's like before a boxing match.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.53,1:39:47.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they don't scurry away he will make them do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.34,1:39:49.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's too intense.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.22,1:39:49.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.17,1:39:50.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,His stare is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.40,1:40:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.61,1:40:00.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,Of course it will.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.55,1:40:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to compare it to boxing?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.35,1:40:02.65,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.40,1:40:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.65,1:40:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with boxing{\alpha&FF} I'm full of confidence before a match.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.84,1:40:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with boxing I'm full of confidence before a match.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.36,1:40:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm full of worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.18,1:40:14.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Takagi meats.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.31,1:40:30.64,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Takagi meats.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.64,1:40:31.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.96,1:40:33.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.81,1:40:35.38,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin please.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.38,1:40:37.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.38,1:40:37.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,She said tenderloin right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.72,1:40:39.69,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin please.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.69,1:40:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.12,1:40:43.16,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tenderloin please.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.16,1:40:44.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.56,1:40:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.51,1:40:50.73,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Shoulder roast please.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.13,1:40:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.73,1:40:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.03,1:40:52.58,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(211.818,50)}Cause they did it 15 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.25,1:40:54.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was able to say both.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.59,1:40:56.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,200 grams.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.35,1:40:58.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,200 grams.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.84,1:40:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,200? Okay please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.02,1:41:02.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them are a nice combination.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.11,1:41:03.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,See? Right on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.89,1:41:06.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Right on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.75,1:41:09.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shoulder roast is for the kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.88,1:41:13.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And 100 gram of the luxurious tenderloin is for their father.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.21,1:41:16.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's high on power but low on fat.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.79,1:41:19.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He often eats it prior to matches.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.49,1:41:22.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And spring onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.50,1:41:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.36,1:41:24.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Spring onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.78,1:41:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring onion?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.33,1:41:25.03,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And spring onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.27,1:41:27.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ririno was able to do her errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.20,1:41:28.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now it's his part.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.17,1:41:32.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother was able to do all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.24,1:41:34.51,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,One please.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.51,1:41:36.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this papa will be ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.56,1:41:39.91,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.41,1:41:42.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can do errands now!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.95,1:41:47.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the brothers responsibility to pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.20,1:41:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.72,1:41:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this is 2500 yen
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.23,1:41:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go get your change.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.68,1:41:53.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.93,1:41:58.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has become a reliable man in no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.70,1:42:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold this.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.22,1:42:03.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ririno takes care of carrying the groceries.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.77,1:42:05.22,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Come come.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.61,1:42:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.74,1:42:07.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.16,1:42:09.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.24,1:42:11.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father is waiting at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.26,1:42:13.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are becoming adults.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.78,1:42:16.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The street to go home is that way however...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.80,1:42:19.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where is Gousuke going?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.92,1:42:23.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If we go that way will we return?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.76,1:42:24.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.68,1:42:29.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameramen are now running in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.41,1:42:29.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.78,1:42:32.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Are they going to the park?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.03,1:42:36.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite having made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.07,1:42:36.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,Where are they going?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.14,1:42:42.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While holding Ririno's hands Gousuke is heading towards...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.14,1:42:44.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay, shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.58,1:42:45.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shrine!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.50,1:42:50.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their father always comes here before a match.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.02,1:42:52.34,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Do not run.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.89,1:42:58.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.31,1:43:00.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What will he wish for?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.08,1:43:09.72,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.44,1:43:19.05,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's hope that father wins his matches again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.05,1:43:21.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How amazing, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.72,1:43:25.77,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Phew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.42,1:43:28.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,He loves his parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.03,1:43:43.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke did the errand to his best so that his father can win his next match.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.37,1:43:45.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,So irresistible.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.53,1:43:53.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wondering why Riri was able to do it today without crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.86,1:43:57.62,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I love papa's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.62,1:43:59.47,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Right, Gouchan?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.67,1:43:59.47,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.47,1:44:01.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.06,1:44:03.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wanted to eat your father's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.56,1:44:09.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both of their errand has been perfectly carried out.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.18,1:44:12.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. Cause they rehearsed 15 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.18,1:44:15.02,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We are almost there.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.67,1:44:17.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,Sparta upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.42,1:44:21.61,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yay, we did our best.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.29,1:44:21.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,Yay, you did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.49,1:44:25.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We are home.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.91,1:44:27.20,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We are home.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.41,1:44:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.20,1:44:29.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so anxious.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.87,1:44:29.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,The way he says "eeh!?".
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.07,1:44:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.55,1:44:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.78,1:44:32.85,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.45,1:44:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.52,1:44:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.59,1:44:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.14,1:44:39.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,At Takagi meats.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.06,1:44:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.68,1:44:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.15,1:44:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.75,1:44:45.48,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.47,1:44:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.74,1:44:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.09,1:44:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Riri. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.09,1:44:53.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.06,1:44:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.62,1:44:54.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.64,1:44:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.26,1:44:58.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He cuts the spring onions using the "God's left".
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.62,1:45:04.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Actually since becoming a pro
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.55,1:45:06.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he's been working part-time at a Ramen joint.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.06,1:45:09.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Skillful movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.16,1:45:12.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 1200 yen 100 grams of tenderloin.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.13,1:45:15.38,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.53,1:45:16.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.93,1:45:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.90,1:45:19.82,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.82,1:45:20.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's their mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.77,1:45:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.90,1:45:23.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.32,1:45:28.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pork shoulder roast and lots of spring onion fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.68,1:45:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.89,1:45:32.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their fathers cooking is like a pros.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.91,1:45:37.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as the soup is also ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.45,1:45:39.70,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.49,1:45:44.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the famous daddy's fried rice that he hasn't been able to make recently.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.86,1:45:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.98,1:45:51.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.24,1:45:51.84,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.90,1:45:55.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For this errand mom worked behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.30,1:45:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat is delicious too.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.94,1:46:00.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He ate the meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.39,1:46:01.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gousuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.39,1:46:03.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He usually doesn't eat meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.00,1:46:07.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ririno eats anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.67,1:46:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah, delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.10,1:46:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa can do his best again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.89,1:46:12.72,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.24,1:46:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.15,1:46:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become strong again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.29,1:46:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next match.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.12,1:46:17.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,One more time?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.76,1:46:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will fight again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.89,1:46:19.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.76,1:46:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.15,1:46:25.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hey hey ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.72,1:46:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Riri.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.77,1:46:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's with your left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.17,1:46:30.12,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,That's your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.12,1:46:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it with your left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.57,1:46:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.77,1:46:35.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. With the "God's left".
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.74,1:46:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa will do his best from here on.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.31,1:46:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Hey hey ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.93,1:46:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With a bigger voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.15,1:46:44.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hey hey ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.67,1:46:44.65,Studio,,0,0,0,,He always makes them do it many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.75,1:46:48.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka gains his strength from... his family.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.12,1:46:51.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Bringing both of them in the ring
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.83,1:46:55.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he will soon again be embracing the two like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.75,1:47:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.52,1:47:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The rice looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.44,1:47:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.38,1:47:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.79,1:47:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,First time seeing this. How is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.83,1:47:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I understimated my son and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.18,1:47:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You made them do it 15 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.53,1:47:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.44,1:47:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just how parents feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.19,1:47:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at the clip
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.51,1:47:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a clear sense that they got it however
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.25,1:47:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I made them do it many times but
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.37,1:47:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel like they didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.94,1:47:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.17,1:47:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They got it by the 2nd or 3rd time.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.07,1:47:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was excessive.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.71,1:47:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even looking at it I was surprised at how persistent I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.28,1:47:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.08,1:47:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Riri practiced it 15 times the moment the doors open she shouted "tenderloin".
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.17,1:47:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.51,1:47:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As the doors were sliding.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.23,1:48:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When they went to the shrine to pray
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.65,1:48:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and said "hope papa will win" and how they were holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.53,1:48:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt so good looking at this imagery.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.18,1:48:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.77,1:48:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I would cry while watching this clip.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.37,1:48:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You could cry at any point.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.32,1:48:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.54,1:48:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright dad,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.98,1:48:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you have an important match coming up. Are you prepared for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.58,1:48:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since my son and daughter did their best
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.53,1:48:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,next is my turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.82,1:48:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.04,1:48:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You better do.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.01,1:48:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be supporting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.51,1:48:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.31,1:48:33.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.13,1:48:35.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An errand while waiting for spring.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.65,1:48:38.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With -20°C in the middle of winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.32,1:48:41.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The frozen plain of Shikaoichou in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.90,1:48:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,572)}Hokkaido ● Shikaoichou
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.07,1:48:42.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From November to April
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.89,1:48:45.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the ground remains covered in snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.27,1:48:49.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Tokachi Plain was first settled 120 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.29,1:48:53.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,People used axes and saws...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.15,1:48:57.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to cut through the thick growth of bamboo grass and oak trees turning it into farmland.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.60,1:48:58.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,What an amazing thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.82,1:49:01.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Anything that can be done will be done by the people themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.87,1:49:06.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That spirit from the pioneer days is still rooted in their daily lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.83,1:49:09.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the long winter comes to an end by the end of April.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.71,1:49:12.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Farmers get busy at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.85,1:49:16.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fields, as far as the eye can see, all belong to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.14,1:49:19.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've lived here for 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.21,1:49:22.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is an errand among huge agricultural fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.48,1:49:27.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their farmlands are larger than Tokyo Disneyland.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.38,1:49:30.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cabbage, wheat, potato and more.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.47,1:49:33.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's another world, like a storybook.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.70,1:49:37.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here lives Mirei and Kaori who are siblings that get along.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.67,1:49:41.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The proper big sister and the shrewd little sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.43,1:49:44.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They help out in the fields every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.25,1:49:47.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are given a lot of freedom by their mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.83,1:49:50.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They know no fear of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.24,1:49:51.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.61,1:49:58.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,at Mirei's house people come to learn about Hokkaido's agriculture from China, Taiwan, Indonesia, Australia and New Zealand.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.86,1:50:01.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,People come to study from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.38,1:50:05.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They eat with the trainees
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.30,1:50:07.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and they live like a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.32,1:50:12.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And next to the log cabin where everyone eats is their home.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.63,1:50:16.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today they are making food for 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.25,1:50:18.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They better go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.75,1:50:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to prepare the stew already.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.93,1:50:21.87,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.29,1:50:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikon.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.49,1:50:25.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are making homemade stew for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.29,1:50:30.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Daikon, onions, carrots.\N All ingredients are from their farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.96,1:50:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What else do we need?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.85,1:50:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't we need potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.98,1:50:35.82,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.82,1:50:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.20,1:50:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get it at the storage?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.32,1:50:37.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.70,1:50:38.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.69,1:50:41.51,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, good luck charms!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.51,1:50:43.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First their errand is to the snow storage.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.43,1:50:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is both of yours job.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.94,1:50:48.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.98,1:50:52.63,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,What's inside the good luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.93,1:50:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.63,1:50:53.40,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Show it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.40,1:50:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I can show that. That's too embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.27,1:51:00.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To commemorate this day
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.39,1:51:02.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she made them yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.48,1:51:04.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.16,1:51:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.31,1:51:07.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama's heart is really heavy, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.11,1:51:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? It's pretty heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.37,1:51:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.95,1:51:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It also has Shiji's feelings in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.59,1:51:14.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will give birth to a younger brother next month.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.14,1:51:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you job right or I will be angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.56,1:51:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play around.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.93,1:51:21.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother moved here from Kyoto after marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.90,1:51:25.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has placed her children in the care of the majestic nature of Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.00,1:51:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relying on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.08,1:51:28.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.38,1:51:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.42,1:51:29.20,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.62,1:51:31.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,One Two One Two
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.29,1:51:34.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are looking for their father to open the snow storage.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.73,1:51:37.71,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder if papa is around.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.99,1:51:37.71,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder if papa is around.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.03,1:51:39.65,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.25,1:51:41.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Asparagus.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.38,1:51:42.48,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.62,1:51:43.35,Studio,,0,0,0,,Growing it on your own is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.50,1:51:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.53,1:51:45.62,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please open the snow storage.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.15,1:51:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.32,1:51:51.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Because mama told us to get potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.44,1:51:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't there any in the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.04,1:51:53.79,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.08,1:51:57.13,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And we got good luck charms.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.93,1:52:01.27,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And mama's feelings{\alpha&FF} are inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.27,1:52:02.65,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And mama's feelings are inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.65,1:52:03.34,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.34,1:52:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be really heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.22,1:52:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your mom does her best.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.81,1:52:09.39,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Doing her best.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.39,1:52:12.43,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,And we will do our best getting the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.15,1:52:19.89,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is all is needed for happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.89,1:52:20.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.70,1:52:21.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's like an anime.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.57,1:52:25.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The snow storage uses natural snow to freeze things.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.38,1:52:29.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The air inside is so refreshingly cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.41,1:52:30.25,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.71,1:52:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.65,1:52:32.67,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.02,1:52:37.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the snow storage the potatoes have been set aside for half a year
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.54,1:52:39.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which makes them really sweet.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.79,1:52:42.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask for just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.86,1:52:45.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the portion.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.01,1:52:46.53,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.05,1:52:47.78,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.78,1:52:49.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.38,1:52:50.72,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's carry it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.95,1:52:51.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.20,1:52:53.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They carry it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.11,1:52:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I have work to do please carry it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.12,1:52:57.97,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.97,1:52:59.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them can carry it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.11,1:53:02.06,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori will be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.06,1:53:04.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where is Kaori heading?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.65,1:53:08.69,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori is running.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.69,1:53:10.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why is she running?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.05,1:53:11.54,Studio,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to carry them?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.67,1:53:14.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It always ends up like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.58,1:53:17.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mirei carries the burden
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.89,1:53:20.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,while her sister does what she wants to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.58,1:53:22.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One could say that she's stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.90,1:53:26.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will shout when things aren't going well.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.15,1:53:30.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry up and help then they will scold you, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.22,1:53:32.63,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori, hold here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.63,1:53:33.51,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.63,1:53:35.75,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,One two and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.95,1:53:38.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. Now both of them are carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.50,1:53:40.47,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Heavy ho, heavy ho.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.47,1:53:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you carry it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.47,1:53:44.67,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Heavy ho, heavy ho.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.46,1:53:49.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they can do this they can also go to the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.74,1:53:51.56,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.74,1:53:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.13,1:53:54.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We brought it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.25,1:53:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.45,1:53:55.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,It was heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.57,1:53:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped out. Wow, you brought so many.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.12,1:53:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What else does our stew need?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.67,1:54:01.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now is the errand for real.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.62,1:54:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that's right. We don't have any milk.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.39,1:54:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get some from Mana's mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.53,1:54:09.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mana's house is a dairy farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.13,1:54:11.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They always get milk in a pot.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.17,1:54:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Mana's and get it half filled up.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.59,1:54:18.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since it will be heavy half is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.39,1:54:21.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To avoid spillage the lid can sit on tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.68,1:54:22.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.61,1:54:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Also get sausages from the "Warm cafe".
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.45,1:54:28.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's pretty far away.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.22,1:54:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi you're the milk minister.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.02,1:54:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Minister of Milk.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.65,1:54:32.55,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,And what about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.55,1:54:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be the minister of Sausages.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.35,1:54:35.76,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,572)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.72,1:54:36.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Delegating the important tasks.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.32,1:54:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Promoted to minister.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.01,1:54:41.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Fatty sausage.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.84,1:54:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, fatty sausage.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.39,1:54:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kao can say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.83,1:54:42.81,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Four of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.50,1:54:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right four. Four fatty sausages.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.58,1:54:46.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has learned her numbers recently.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.22,1:54:50.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will get milk at their neighbors'.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.92,1:54:52.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which is about 1 kilometer away.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.27,1:54:56.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the closest shop is 2 kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.91,1:55:00.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where they will get 4 packs of sausages.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.21,1:55:02.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Hokkaido is so big.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.70,1:55:02.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Huge.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.25,1:55:03.07,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Heading off.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.07,1:55:07.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they don't get it before 8 the pickup truck will be there ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.30,1:55:08.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.02,1:55:12.66,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I have the duty of a mother towards you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.73,1:55:14.54,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Heavy ho. Heavy ho.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.63,1:55:14.54,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Heavy ho.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.54,1:55:17.33,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Errand. Errand. Err
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.33,1:55:18.13,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Heavy ho.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.13,1:55:18.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.90,1:55:20.43,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Say: Errand. Errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.77,1:55:23.37,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.77,1:55:23.37,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.37,1:55:26.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori is bringing potatoes as thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.31,1:55:28.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And her sister is bringing the pot.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.18,1:55:30.08,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.08,1:55:33.05,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry the milk truck will leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.29,1:55:37.78,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(193.455,324.546)}Mana's house
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.06,1:55:34.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this pace they will make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.86,1:55:37.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They can't see a sign of the big truck yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.30,1:55:40.67,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.89,1:55:41.94,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.94,1:55:43.51,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.21,1:55:44.89,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's becoming homesick.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.64,1:55:46.69,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,You can't go after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.06,1:55:48.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.50,1:55:52.65,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori, you are my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.65,1:55:54.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since you are my little sister act properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.15,1:55:57.34,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mana's house is straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.55,1:56:01.98,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I wanna go by bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.24,1:56:01.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.53,1:56:05.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The three wheeled bike is for people who can't walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.53,1:56:08.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,That's only for adults.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.85,1:56:11.48,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,What about this kid. Can't they walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.48,1:56:12.72,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.52,1:56:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(225.454,187.818)}Veteran staff member
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.72,1:56:14.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, this person can't walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.32,1:56:16.41,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The old man and old lady
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.41,1:56:18.66,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,they usually can't walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.71,1:56:19.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,The old man and lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.99,1:56:20.26,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.86,1:56:22.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,That's why a three-wheeler
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.90,1:56:24.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,is faster but
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.43,1:56:26.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.28,1:56:26.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,She was curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.15,1:56:29.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two young ones started walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.04,1:56:32.01,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Inside of the good luck charm
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.22,1:56:35.68,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,mom's heart and the gods are in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.68,1:56:37.84,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,The gods?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.84,1:56:37.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.84,1:56:40.85,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori loves the gods.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.85,1:56:43.92,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Right? That's why I'm telling you to run.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.78,1:56:46.59,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I will run now.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.59,1:56:47.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,See? {\alphaff}You've become energized.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.84,1:56:50.24,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,See? You've become energized.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.21,1:56:50.24,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.24,1:56:53.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as they've become energized and all is fine...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.63,1:56:56.95,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Miiilk and...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.81,1:56:57.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's so far.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.95,1:56:58.97,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,potatoes
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.28,1:57:02.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While it has become Spring it's still only 3°C.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.04,1:57:05.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The weather is rather volatile.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.56,1:57:08.07,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Everything is tasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.07,1:57:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.23,1:57:11.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.29,1:57:13.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mana's house is a lifestock farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.58,1:57:13.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,They've finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.46,1:57:15.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They always get their milk from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.47,1:57:18.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have a great neighborly relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.47,1:57:20.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This house also delivers the neighborhood circulars.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.05,1:57:23.09,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mana's mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.09,1:57:24.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mana goes to the same kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.84,1:57:27.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori delivers the cold-stored potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.39,1:57:31.06,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Here it is. Potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.70,1:57:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.10,1:57:32.50,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Fill it half up
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.50,1:57:34.23,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,with milk, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.23,1:57:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Half filled with milk. Let me pour some.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.25,1:57:40.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mana's place is a dairy farm of the latest style.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.67,1:57:42.24,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.09,1:57:45.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cows go the milking machines by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.58,1:57:50.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as they go round like a merry-go-round they will be completely milked in no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.98,1:57:53.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And this freshly squeezed milk
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.22,1:57:56.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is collected in a tank in the adjacent room.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.36,1:58:01.31,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Ew.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.31,1:58:02.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.11,1:58:03.90,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's warm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.90,1:58:06.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Big sister with the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.22,1:58:08.02,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fine with this much.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.02,1:58:10.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's so cold outside that the lens is getting foggy.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.84,1:58:13.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They asked for half so that they can carry it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.74,1:58:15.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.56,1:58:15.21,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's pouring.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.21,1:58:16.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.81,1:58:19.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's why they're using a pot.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.31,1:58:21.20,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Who poured this?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.20,1:58:24.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By gathering it from the cows it adds up to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.15,1:58:26.69,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.69,1:58:28.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Too much and it becomes too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.79,1:58:30.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.52,1:58:30.52,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.44,1:58:35.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The condensation from the fresh milk is covering the lens.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.88,1:58:38.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's bring it home.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.63,1:58:42.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The made it before the 8 o'clock truck arrives.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.69,1:58:45.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected from the minister of milk responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.26,1:58:47.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next are the sausages.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.61,1:58:48.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.32,1:58:49.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about the milk?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.88,1:58:50.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.08,1:58:50.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,- The milk?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.88,1:58:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.21,1:58:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna bring it?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.71,1:58:55.52,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please keep it for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.05,1:58:57.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,She will keep it?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.80,1:59:02.26,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,When we come back please hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.79,1:59:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going now?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.09,1:59:06.56,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The "Warm cafe".
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.43,1:59:09.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.66,1:59:14.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Going to the closest shop the "Warm cafe" is all the way over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.78,1:59:19.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. It's better to leave the milk\N in their care and take it on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.62,1:59:19.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.52,1:59:21.27,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,We are heading off.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.27,1:59:24.69,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,We will fill this bag up with sausages.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.69,1:59:26.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the minister of sausages.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.69,1:59:27.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, 4 packages.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.78,1:59:28.63,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.18,1:59:31.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, minister.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.07,1:59:34.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.52,1:59:38.58,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It was a great success.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.58,1:59:40.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They also gave the potatoes
Dialogue: 0,1:59:40.44,1:59:42.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the pot is ready for pickup.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.31,1:59:44.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They finally feel agile.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.86,1:59:45.35,Studio,,0,0,0,,They've become light.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.98,1:59:48.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.14,1:59:52.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The truck that takes the milk.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.56,1:59:55.59,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,How great. How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.74,1:59:58.85,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.98,2:00:02.37,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Today is great.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.37,2:00:05.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori is dragging behind.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.15,2:00:09.09,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Michan, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.75,2:00:09.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.09,2:00:10.32,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.52,2:00:12.53,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.08,2:00:14.03,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.03,2:00:17.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite their age difference their personalities are similar.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.21,2:00:21.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though Kaori can do it she pretends not being able to.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.57,2:00:24.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The little sister likes to be treated sweetly.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.35,2:00:26.24,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go all the way there.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.77,2:00:28.06,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go. A bit further.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.06,2:00:32.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Big sister can't help but look after her little sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.50,2:00:33.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,The big sister is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.02,2:00:43.09,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Who is walking to the "Warm cafe"?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.75,2:00:43.09,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.96,2:00:48.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cows of the "Warm cafe".
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.65,2:00:52.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The owner, Sei, is very kind and is loved by both of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.83,2:00:53.67,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,She's looking.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.67,2:00:56.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where your soul can take a respite and warm up: Warm cafe.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.54,2:00:58.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will purchase the homemade sausages.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.97,2:01:02.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The minister of sausages is the little sister: Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.68,2:01:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.26,2:01:05.91,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Seichan.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.91,2:01:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Seichan. Good day.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.45,2:01:08.92,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Seichan.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.92,2:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What about mama?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.63,2:01:12.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.20,2:01:13.30,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.77,2:01:14.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.55,2:01:16.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The minister has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.09,2:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.53,2:01:21.38,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Minister of sausages.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.16,2:01:21.38,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.69,2:01:23.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.86,2:01:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.07,2:01:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about mama?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.23,2:01:32.09,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama has sent us on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.09,2:01:33.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sei is giving them a wet towel.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.81,2:01:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is mama not coming? Just you two?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.18,2:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you helping out?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.03,2:01:40.85,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Everytime we get hurt
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.85,2:01:42.80,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,she worries about us.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.80,2:01:45.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Minister of sausages. Please step up.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.15,2:01:47.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.30,2:01:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.07,2:01:50.24,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Fatty sausages please.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.24,2:01:52.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her big sister said it instead.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.58,2:01:54.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.56,2:01:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,4 packages?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.05,2:01:57.13,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,600)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.10,2:01:57.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,She was able to say it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.43,2:01:58.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she was still able to say how many.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.68,2:02:00.30,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Money. Money.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.30,2:02:03.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The minister of sausages is carrying the money.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.39,2:02:04.57,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Money.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:04.57,2:02:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.72,2:02:07.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.32,2:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you giving me all this?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.61,2:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 2000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.55,2:02:17.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,Seichan is making such a shady expression.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.55,2:02:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One is 700 yen.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.52,2:02:21.42,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,700 yen?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.72,2:02:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.42,2:02:23.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One package is 700 yen.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.09,2:02:24.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Not enough?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.99,2:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.79,2:02:29.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are four but these aren't the four to get.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.15,2:02:31.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Four packages.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.90,2:02:33.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2000 yen is just not enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.03,2:02:34.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.85,2:02:37.49,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,What will we do. We can't go home without it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.49,2:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can't go home.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.31,2:02:42.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their mother has miscalculated it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.04,2:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since 2000 yen isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.91,2:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.51,2:02:48.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Giving them less or...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.27,2:02:51.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will Seichan give them for free?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.32,2:02:52.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,Seichan. Seichan.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.67,2:02:54.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One of these two.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.02,2:02:54.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's curious.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.64,2:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For the insufficient part
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.16,2:03:00.03,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.03,2:03:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.89,2:03:04.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a weird feeling.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.46,2:03:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:05.10,2:03:07.03,Studio,,0,0,0,,Weird feeling.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.88,2:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I will just get it from your mother later.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.00,2:03:11.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally a new proposal.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.87,2:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I will write down the missing amount.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.02,2:03:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,800 yen.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.34,2:03:19.16,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,800 yen, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.16,2:03:21.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seichan is so gentle.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.97,2:03:25.50,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Oh no. This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.50,2:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it started raining.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.25,2:03:30.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not only cold but it has started raining.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.21,2:03:33.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not only cold but it has started raining.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.58,2:03:38.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seicchan is dressing them in the raincoats from their bags.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.25,2:03:41.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And he's giving them hot patches to warm them up.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.58,2:03:41.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.07,2:03:43.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seichan is so kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.97,2:03:48.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Further more, further more. He's also giving them warm milk for free.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.72,2:03:48.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,How good.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.89,2:03:50.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.51,2:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaori and Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.88,2:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The milk is ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.88,2:03:56.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.85,2:03:58.15,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.57,2:04:04.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It melts.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.96,2:04:06.93,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.02,2:04:06.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a nice face.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.31,2:04:07.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.84,2:04:10.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori is also enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.43,2:04:12.83,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.23,2:04:15.14,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Old man, are you also cold?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.14,2:04:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.12,2:04:17.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It looks cold.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.44,2:04:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.42,2:04:20.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,So kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.57,2:04:20.49,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.49,2:04:21.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Giving it to the man?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.57,2:04:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.81,2:04:23.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,So kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.38,2:04:29.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori has been influenced by Seichans kindness.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.54,2:04:34.65,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Micchan give yours.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.90,2:04:38.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Kaori's kindness has been conveyed to her sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.42,2:04:39.73,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Warm dr...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.73,2:04:41.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's even giving hers to the camera man.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.93,2:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.43,2:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.28,2:04:49.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A chain of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.92,2:04:51.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone is feeling warm and fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.90,2:04:53.94,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Seichan, I drank it all.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.90,2:04:53.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.94,2:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.04,2:04:56.91,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It was warm and delicious.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.44,2:05:01.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the cafe they've become warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.58,2:05:02.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.95,2:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.67,2:05:08.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.99,2:05:10.99,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.99,2:05:13.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.76,2:05:16.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them are departing with renewed energy.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.68,2:05:18.46,Studio,,0,0,0,,Seichan is becoming soaked.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.26,2:05:18.97,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.97,2:05:19.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that instant
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.28,2:05:23.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the rain has become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.90,2:05:26.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is normal in early spring.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.81,2:05:29.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite having warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.18,2:05:31.24,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.33,2:05:31.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,- It's pouring down.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.88,2:05:31.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Looks cold.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.73,2:05:32.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Looks cold.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.95,2:05:35.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's so cold that the lens has fogged up again.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.85,2:05:38.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the harsh nature of Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.33,2:05:40.62,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.52,2:05:40.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are soaked.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.85,2:05:43.06,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,If we don't go.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.51,2:05:45.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.26,2:05:48.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister can't go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.83,2:05:50.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's looking at Kaori's face
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.70,2:05:52.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and adjusting her pace
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.42,2:05:53.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,while encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.82,2:05:56.04,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.82,2:05:59.47,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I can only do a tiny bit of my best.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.47,2:06:00.14,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.37,2:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's honest.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.36,2:06:04.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Will you go home?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.53,2:06:04.64,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.34,2:06:07.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"But Kaori can still go on"
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.96,2:06:09.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is what her sister felt.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:11.10,2:06:13.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We don't need the milk?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.29,2:06:15.82,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:17.37,2:06:18.37,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.37,2:06:20.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their mother always tells them
Dialogue: 0,2:06:20.16,2:06:22.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"It's more fun to give it your all."
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.28,2:06:22.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.11,2:06:27.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Do our best. Do our best. Do our best.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.28,2:06:29.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mana's house is within sight.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.67,2:06:32.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will get the milk and take it back home.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.64,2:06:36.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.46,2:06:38.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's warm again.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.53,2:06:40.58,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.58,2:06:42.75,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's here. On top.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.75,2:06:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take it?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:45.75,2:06:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Mirei do your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:50.72,2:06:53.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister carries the milk.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.48,2:06:53.73,Studio,,0,0,0,,Hard.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.14,2:06:55.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori is carrying 4 packages of sausages.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.71,2:06:57.33,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.56,2:06:59.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone is bringing home their own things.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.35,2:07:01.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,You would get tired from this.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.25,2:07:01.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their house is within sight.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.02,2:07:03.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.30,2:07:08.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their mother is waiting for them on the road.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.44,2:07:12.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they turn around here their mother is waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.75,2:07:16.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If she can power through then it's just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.63,2:07:16.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, the milk is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.82,2:07:17.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,It must be.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.00,2:07:18.25,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.40,2:07:20.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wants to go to them
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.10,2:07:23.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but she's holding that in.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.72,2:07:26.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Better than quitting, exerting yourself is the way.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.56,2:07:28.46,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.46,2:07:31.45,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's better to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.45,2:07:33.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At first she could easily carry it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.13,2:07:36.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it has become heavy.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.38,2:07:49.02,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.02,2:07:51.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori kept looking over her.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.35,2:07:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.79,2:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.52,2:07:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.51,2:08:01.43,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.09,2:08:03.28,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.28,2:08:07.05,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Michan is crying.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.24,2:08:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei, do your best. I'm waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.25,2:08:12.89,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.91,2:08:15.88,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright, wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.88,2:08:17.53,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I will walk over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.53,2:08:19.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Big sister, I will do something for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.41,2:08:23.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori has forgotten how heavy her own bag is
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.38,2:08:25.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and is completely focused on her sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.23,2:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.13,2:08:39.50,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mirei can't carry it.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:40.20,2:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't carry it?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:42.47,2:08:45.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wanting to convey to her mother about her sisters situation
Dialogue: 0,2:08:45.74,2:08:48.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she's made it to the goal without even paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.67,2:08:50.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sausages have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.01,2:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:53.01,2:08:53.61,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.23,2:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Micchan is still sitting over there. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.02,2:09:02.05,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Because Michan is exhausted
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.05,2:09:05.36,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I came to mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:05.36,2:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to tell me? \NThat Michan is exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.83,2:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:13.62,2:09:14.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.93,2:09:17.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,becomes decisive while seeing her sisters resolution.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.46,2:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.00,2:09:35.25,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's better to give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.82,2:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Michan.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.16,2:09:40.13,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Michan.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.13,2:09:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa and mama are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.63,2:09:44.43,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm doing my best walking over.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.43,2:09:46.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papa was watching while hiding.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.55,2:09:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei come over here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.50,2:09:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this the goal.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.39,2:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.93,2:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.16,2:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.99,2:10:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.80,2:10:09.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.82,2:10:10.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the goal.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.41,2:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mama has...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.99,2:10:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the milk all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.17,2:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was heavy, wasn't it? You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.30,2:10:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.92,2:10:26.87,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori also did her best.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:26.87,2:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.56,2:10:32.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was truly better to have given it their all.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:32.95,2:10:34.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You were remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.65,2:10:37.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's go home. To a warm place.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.17,2:10:44.02,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Since Kaori went to mama
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.02,2:10:47.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I became decisive
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.28,2:10:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You became decisive?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.00,2:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.81,2:10:53.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them were able to do it till the end.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.30,2:10:57.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was cold but everyone was warm.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.74,2:11:02.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today's sausage stew will be a warm stew.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.78,2:11:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.71,2:11:07.80,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:07.80,2:11:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.20,2:11:10.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's done.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.20,2:11:09.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,There are so much sausage in it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:14.15,2:11:20.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are bringing it over to eat with the helping hands from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.36,2:11:22.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The stew is done.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.36,2:11:24.26,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,The stew is done.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.26,2:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.38,2:11:27.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The camera is fogging up again.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.30,2:11:31.20,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.44,2:11:33.84,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Everyone try and taste it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:33.84,2:11:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.99,2:11:38.41,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Sausage. Sausage.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.08,2:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the sausage...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.71,2:11:40.01,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.01,2:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.53,2:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.40,2:11:43.63,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.63,2:11:45.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The minister of sausages.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.02,2:11:47.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.75,2:11:51.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,thank you to the minister of milk.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.67,2:11:55.06,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Today I will sleep all day.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.06,2:11:56.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.90,2:11:56.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so tired.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.85,2:11:58.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,Because she's tired.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.70,2:11:58.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next is spring
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.18,2:12:02.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and after the short Hokkaido summer
Dialogue: 0,2:12:04.30,2:12:08.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and then they will be back to the harsh winter.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.42,2:12:10.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Due to the coldness of midwinter
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.59,2:12:13.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The nature raises you to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.06,2:12:15.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.31,2:12:17.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their younger brother Shinji was born.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.48,2:12:22.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them will help out lots from now on.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:42.22,2:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The grandness of Hokkaido sure is nice.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.51,2:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:45.93,2:12:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But the mother is remarkable too.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.78,2:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Insisting on not going over to her
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.25,2:12:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but to declare her place as the goal.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.84,2:12:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This type of mother and father
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.76,2:13:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,will raise children who are happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:02.75,2:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only just saying that "doing your best is better" but they get to watch their parents constantly doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.34,2:13:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a big sister and we have a lot of fun together.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.62,2:13:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I think that things are tough just seeing my mother gave me a sense of security.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:21.01,2:13:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of security at home
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.77,2:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is truly something worth appreciating.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:26.34,2:13:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To look up to your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.15,2:13:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It really influenced me.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.47,2:13:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It really influenced you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.89,2:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For the last goal
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.92,2:13:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamanaka papa, would you wait it out?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:33.78,2:13:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I would go right away.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.98,2:13:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I would.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:38.70,2:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If this entire segment was Yamanaka and his children then they wouldn't even start.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:44.34,2:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't even work.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:44.64,2:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't even work.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.39,2:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.84,2:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(602,618)}Yamanashi ● Katsunuma-budoukyo
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.48,2:13:52.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The closest JR station is Katsunuma-budoukyo station.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.80,2:13:55.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is also the birthplace of Japanese wine.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.08,2:13:59.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During autumn many tourists come to pick grapes.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:59.67,2:14:03.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Three siblings have grown up at this vineyard.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.61,2:14:07.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The ones going on an errand is the 2nd and the 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:07.74,2:14:12.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori who can take care of those below her is hoping to be the mature older sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:12.65,2:14:16.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kozue just wants to be strong and happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:17.02,2:14:21.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For the grape picking customers, miso soup is offered for free.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.12,2:14:23.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Bringing the empty bowls back is how they help.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:23.54,2:14:25.73,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Kozue doesn't bring them back.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:23.54,2:14:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.73,2:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.41,2:14:29.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's not enough tofu for the next customers.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.30,2:14:31.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.00,2:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go and buy some tofu?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.24,2:14:35.17,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Five packages.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:35.17,2:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Five packages if they are small
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.12,2:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but if they are large then five will be too heavy so only get three.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.68,2:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know that grandma needs her hip medicine...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.30,2:14:45.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.23,2:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that she rubs on. If you mention it they will know.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.80,2:14:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the pharmacy.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.07,2:14:53.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.95,2:14:53.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,Her explanation is kind of crude.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.16,2:14:58.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the pharmacy she needs to get medicine for her grandma
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.13,2:15:02.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and tofu at the supermarket. Today is the grape festival so there will be many people.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.55,2:15:05.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The town is different today.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.83,2:15:09.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the once-a-year grape festival.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.76,2:15:13.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sound of fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.86,2:15:18.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big sister always reacts poorly to loud noises.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.76,2:15:14.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,She looks surprised.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.41,2:15:24.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On top of her first errand the loud sounds are reverberating.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:25.49,2:15:26.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:27.56,2:15:30.69,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,The always crying kitten...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:30.69,2:15:33.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's not true Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.40,2:15:36.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The portable shrine has come out.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.58,2:15:38.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The adults are shouting loudly
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.48,2:15:41.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and big sister's heart pounds even harder.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.42,2:15:45.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are surrounded by a wall of butts.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.96,2:15:52.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While dragging her little brother by the hand they've finally arrived at the pharmacy.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.00,2:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you two come by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:57.07,2:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.49,2:16:01.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's medicine for her grandmas hips.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:01.07,2:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you come to purchase?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:04.33,2:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:05.61,2:16:08.75,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,You rub on your buttocks...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:08.11,2:16:09.28,Studio,,0,0,0,,Buttocks?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:08.75,2:16:11.12,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Grandma. Buttocks.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:11.12,2:16:15.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,599)}That you rub on, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:11.23,2:16:13.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,For her grandmas buttocks?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.85,2:16:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. For your grandmas behind.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.87,2:16:16.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,TEXT5
Dialogue: 0,2:16:16.84,2:16:20.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not for her buttocks but her hips.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:20.66,2:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Close.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:24.58,2:16:28.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Must be based on the view.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:29.15,2:16:31.15,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, because that's all she saw on her way.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:31.97,2:16:35.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, she gave her hemorrhoid cream.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.81,2:16:37.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And they purchased it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:37.93,2:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring the reward. Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.84,2:16:41.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Even though she doesn't have hemorrhoids.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:40.13,2:16:42.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady always gives them something.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:42.70,2:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.28,2:16:45.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today is big.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:45.88,2:16:47.72,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.72,2:16:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mandarins and manjuu buns.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.91,2:16:50.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:50.31,2:16:53.99,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,593)}Manjyuu?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.79,2:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You going to be okay? Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.99,2:16:56.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Big sister doesn't have the composure to give thanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.66,2:16:58.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sorry old lady.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:00.38,2:17:03.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've arrived at the supermarket. They will get tofu.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.85,2:17:06.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are policemen everywhere because of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:08.44,2:17:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.19,2:17:12.18,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please help us cross.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.71,2:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's oka... huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:12.18,2:17:14.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please help us cross.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:12.81,2:17:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Help you cross? Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:14.86,2:17:18.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has calmed down and finally acting like a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.30,2:17:20.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,Please help us cross.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:20.70,2:17:21.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,She said it properly.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.19,2:17:27.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother told her to ask the cashier where the tofu is.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.99,2:17:31.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she doesn't know when to ask.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:31.66,2:17:33.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's difficult indeed.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.42,2:17:39.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She waited 10 minutes for the customers to leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.92,2:17:42.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Where's the tofu?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:42.31,2:17:44.23,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Where's the to...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:44.69,2:17:46.85,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Where's the tofu?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:46.85,2:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to the furthest in this direction.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:50.73,2:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:51.50,2:17:53.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She finally asked.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.34,2:17:56.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they are small then five packages
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.57,2:17:59.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,or three of the big ones.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:59.59,2:18:03.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has picked the big ones.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:03.90,2:18:07.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are given to the grape picking customers.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.28,2:18:05.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:07.32,2:18:09.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They're expecting a big group today.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:11.24,2:18:14.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They won't get any rewards here.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.93,2:18:20.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are taking a route back where cars don't go.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.70,2:18:23.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the road her mother told her to take...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.78,2:18:26.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is overflowing with people.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:26.35,2:18:31.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother forgot about all the stalls filling up the road.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.71,2:18:32.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,Makes you hungry.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:31.57,2:18:36.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sister is always really interested in toys but not today.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.41,2:18:39.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Kozue can't take his eyes away.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.98,2:18:41.63,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's all so seducing.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:43.77,2:18:47.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, don't get carried away and dance along.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.09,2:18:49.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,I get this mood.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.86,2:18:52.56,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.43,2:18:56.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've finally beat the crowds.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:59.23,2:19:02.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not like Kozue is walking fast
Dialogue: 0,2:19:02.05,2:19:05.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it's the sister who is becoming slower and slower.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.12,2:19:06.81,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.81,2:19:08.43,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:10.73,2:19:14.27,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori the doooog
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.30,2:19:17.84,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,is in trouble woof woof wooof
Dialogue: 0,2:19:17.84,2:19:20.79,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,woof woof wooof
Dialogue: 0,2:19:22.52,2:19:25.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Among the three siblings the sister is the most prone to crying
Dialogue: 0,2:19:25.98,2:19:27.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that's what the mother told us.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.85,2:19:31.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But even when she cries she carries out her duty till the end.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.77,2:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:41.29,2:19:44.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Suddenly her legs stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:44.75,2:19:46.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Kozue only looks forward.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:47.22,2:19:49.38,Studio,,0,0,0,,Please notice her.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.38,2:19:49.38,Studio,,0,0,0,,Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:49.15,2:19:50.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Aah, he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.35,2:19:54.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kozue who only looks forward.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:54.24,2:19:55.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Aah, he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:03.35,2:20:05.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He runs to her in full force.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:10.67,2:20:12.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And tells her this:
Dialogue: 0,2:20:13.34,2:20:14.83,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.23,2:20:34.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kozue is matching his pace with his sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.32,2:20:40.02,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.02,2:20:42.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't help carry the bags.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.47,2:20:48.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And his sister insists on carrying them herself.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:52.28,2:20:54.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them alone in the grape fields
Dialogue: 0,2:20:54.72,2:20:58.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,arriving in the twilight of the mountain region.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.57,2:21:01.94,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.97,2:21:03.61,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mom is there.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.91,2:21:07.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They live in a grape field.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.63,2:21:10.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a shortcut to the front door.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.69,2:21:19.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their mother has turned on all the lights in the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:21.86,2:21:24.71,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Kaori cried.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:26.33,2:21:29.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if she cried, she still did it till the end.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.57,2:21:33.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kozue is tough even though he's only 2.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:37.29,2:21:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the drug?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:38.84,2:21:40.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's hemorrhoid medicine.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.20,2:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.65,2:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.37,2:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for some cream for grandmas hips, this is slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.09,2:21:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.77,2:21:53.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The customer have gone home for today but
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.46,2:21:57.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the mother is making her specialty miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.00,2:22:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.15,2:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.39,2:22:12.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,22 years have passed since then...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:14.41,2:22:15.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A wedding!?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.23,2:22:17.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which means?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.28,2:22:18.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which one, which one.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.52,2:22:20.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori is 27 years by now.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:20.25,2:22:22.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kozue is 25 years old.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:23.00,2:22:24.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:23.61,2:22:24.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.34,2:22:30.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the younger brother Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.06,2:22:32.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.03,2:22:35.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's marrying someone cool.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:35.47,2:22:37.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:38.50,2:22:40.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was just 2 year old
Dialogue: 0,2:22:41.09,2:22:43.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.02,2:22:46.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and in no time 22 years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.28,2:22:47.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.03,2:22:52.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Grown to a spectacular 1.85 cm.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:52.12,2:22:56.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's tall and they've met at a volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.89,2:23:00.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't help you carry anything back then.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:00.36,2:23:02.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has apologized by now.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.81,2:23:03.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.93,2:23:05.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where is his big sister?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:06.92,2:23:08.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:10.97,2:23:14.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kaori hasn't married yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:14.01,2:23:14.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:14.87,2:23:16.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Working as a travel agent
Dialogue: 0,2:23:17.13,2:23:21.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She lives on her own and helps out at the vineyard on her days off.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:21.50,2:23:25.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one sibling who does it till the end even through tears
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.60,2:23:28.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she still helps out at home.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.54,2:23:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel like continuing to help out here?
